\imt1 Akar faragha zuim 
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam, a Samuel…®n Ak…®nafarir Namba 2…®n eghaghanibar g…®n otivizir bizibagh eghari. An Atrivim Devit…®n ik…®r…®m…®rir abuananam geghari. An Atrivim Solomon…®n ik…®r…®m…®rim ko ingangaribagh eghara, egha uaghan, Israelia uan kantri abigha kantrin pumuning…®n otozim…®n dughiam…®n, an aning gativazir atrivibagh eghari. Egha uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mabar eghaghaniba uaghan an iti. Me God…®n akaba isa atriviba ko gumazamiziba tuavir aghuim…®n g…®n mangasa, men akakagha me m…®gei. God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar mav, a Elaija. 
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam, mati Samuel…®n Ak…®nafarir Namba 1 ko Namba 2. A pura eghaghanir k…®nim puvat…®. An atriviba amizir bizibagh eghara uaghan men araziba tuis…®si. Atrivir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n apengan itiba, me ziar aghuiba iti, egha me atrivibar itir dughiabar, Israelia men apengan ikia deraghav…®ra iti. Ez…® atrivir God…®n akaba batoziba, me ziar kuraba iti. Egha me atrivibar itir dughiabar, Israelian dabirabim ikufi. Atriviba arazir kurar kam gami. Me asebar ziaba fasa tintinibar m…®ghs…®abar ghuavanadi. Men arazir kam God gamima, a bar men oseme. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Solomon Israelian atrivim…®n iti 
\mr (Sapta 1--11) 
\s1 Atrivim Devit bar ghuri 
\p  
\v 1 Atrivim Devit bar ghuriz…®, an m…®karzim zurarama arugharusi. Ez…® me inir m…®tiar avagha akuiba isava anevema, da tong fefem a gan…®dir puvat…®.  
\v 2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an ingangarir gumazir dapaniba a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim, en gumazir ekiam, e ti n…® bagh guivir igiatam inight…®, a n…® ko ik…® n…®n akurvagh deragh n…®n ganam. Egh a n…® muigh daku egh n…®n m…®karzim fefem a dan…®ngam.‚Äù  
\v 3 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me kantri Israel…®n danganiba bar, dar amizir igiar bar diriba bagha ruiagha arui. Egha Sunem…®n nguibam…®n amizim, Abisak, an apigha, a inigha atrivim bagha ize.  
\v 4 Amizir bar igiar dirir kam…®n ganganiba bar dera, a bar deraghav…®ra atrivim…®n akurvagha an gara a geghufi. Ez…® Atrivim Devit tong poroghamiba uari ko akuava amir arazitam…®n a gamizir puvat…®. 
\s1 Adoniya atrivim…®n otivasa 
\p  
\v 5-6 \x - \xo 1:5-6 \xt 2 Samuel 3:4\x*Adoniya, a Devit ko Hagit…®n otarim. Hagit Apsalom bategha, an g…®rara Adoniya bate. Adoniyan ganganiba bar dera, ez…® an afeziam bar fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, dughiatam…®n tong an arazir kuratam bagha an azangs…®gha kamagh…®n a m…®kemezir puvat…®, ‚ÄúN…® manmaghsua arazir kabagh ami?‚Äù Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n Adoniya uab…®, uab…® fa ghaze, an atrivim…®n otivam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a m…®dorozir karisba ko hoziaba ko 50plan gumazir a geghuv an faragh mangamiba ini.  
\v 7 Egha a ghua Seruian otarim Joap, ko ofa gamir gumazim Abiatar, aning ko m…®kemez…®ma, aning an akuraght…® an atrivim…®n otivasa aning ifonge.  
\v 8 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazim Sadok, ko Jehoiadan otarim Benaia, ko akam inigh izir gumazim Natan, ko Simei, ko Rei, ko atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba, me Adoniyan n…®ghn…®zim ko itir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 9 Dughiar mam…®n. Adoniya ofa damuasa danganir mam…®n ghu, danganir kam, me kamagh…®n a d…®bora ghaze, Kuruzibar Dag…®am, a Enrogel…®n nguazim…®n aven anadir d…®par atuim…®n borogh…®n iti. A sipsipba ko bulmakaun apuriba ko bulmakaun igiar m…®karziba sara itibav suegha ofa gami. A izasa atrivim…®n otarir igharaziba, ko Judan atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazir dapaniba, ko atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazir igharaziba me bagha akam amada.  
\v 10 Egha an akam inigha izir gumazim Natan, ko Benaia, ko atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba, ko an aveghbuam Solomon, a me bagha akatam amadazir puvat…®. 
\s1 Solomon atrivim…®n oto 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt 2 Samuel 12:24\x*Ez…® akam inigha izir gumazim Natan, a Solomon…®n amebam Batseba bagha ghua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n oraghiz, o puvat…®, Hagit…®n otarim, Adoniya, Atrivim Devit…®n danganim inigh atrivim…®n otivasava ami. Ez…® en gumazir ekiam Devit, bizir kam g…®fozir puvat…®.  
\v 12 Kamagh…®n, n…® uan otarim Solomon ko, gua uaghara aremeghan koghs…®, k…® gua m…®k…®mamin akabar g…®rara mang…® dar amuam.  
\v 13 N…® bar zuam…®ra Atrivim Devit bagh mang…® kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòAtrivim, nan gumazir ekiam, k…® n…®n ingangarir amizim. N…® na ko faragha akam ak…®ra kamagh…®n m…®keme, n…®n otarim Solomon g…®n nan danganim inigh atrivim…®n otogh, nan atrivir dabirabim dapiam. Ez…® manmagh…®n amiz…®, Adoniya dat…®r…®gh…®n atrivim…®n oto?‚Äô  
\v 14 Dughiar n…® mang…® Atrivim Devit ko m…®k…®mv…®ra ikiamim…®n, k…® aven iz…® gavgavim n…®n akam dan…®ng, n…® m…®gei mogh…®ra m…®k…®mam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® Batseba atrivim…®n ganasa atrivim akui nagh…®n a gat…®n aven ghu. Atrivim Devit bar ghuri, ez…® Sunemian amizim Abisak, a geghuva deragha an gari.  
\v 16 Ez…® Batseba atrivim…®n guam…®n uan tevimning ap…®righa guam aviraz…®, atrivim an azara, ‚ÄúN…® bizir tizim gifongegha na bagha izi?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® Batseba a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúNan gumazir ekiam, k…® n…®n ingangarir amizim. N…® fom…®ra akar mam Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a n…®n God, an ziam…®n na koma anek…®ra ghaze, nan otarim Solomon n…®n danganim inigh atrivim…®n otogh, n…®n atrivir dabirabim dapiam.  
\v 18 Ez…® n…® oragh! Atrivim, nan gumazir ekiam. Adoniya dat…®r…®gh…®n atrivim…®n oto. Ez…® n…® ti tong kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®.  
\v 19 A bulmakaun apuriba ko, bulmakaun igiar m…®karziba sara itiba ko, sipsip…®n av…®ribav suegha ofa gami. Egha n…®n otariba ko ofa gamir gumazim Abiatar ko m…®dorozir gumazibar faragha zuir gumazim Joap, a me bagha akaba amangiz…® me ghue. Egha n…®n ingangarir gumazim Solomon, an a bagh akatam amadazir puvat…®.  
\v 20 O atrivim, nan gumazir ekiam, Israelian gumazamiziba bar n…®rara gara n…® m…®zua iti, n…® uab…® gumazir manatam am…®seveght…®, a n…®n danganim inigh atrivim…®n otogh, egh atrivir dabirabim dapiam.  
\v 21 Puvat…®ght…®, n…® aremegh mang…® uan inazir afeziaba iti nagh…®n me ko ik…®t…®, gumazamiziba k…® uan otarim Solomon ko kamagh…®n ga m…®k…®mam, ga gumazim ko amizir kuramning. Egh me ga m…®sueght…® ga aremegham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 22 Egha Batseba m…®g…®av…®ra itima, akam inigha izir gumazim Natan iza atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n oto.  
\v 23 Ez…® Atrivim Devit…®n ingangarir gumaziba ghua a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAkam inigha izir gumazim Natan izegha n…®n ganasa.‚Äù Ez…® atrivim an amamangat…®z…®, Natan atrivim akui nagh…®n a gat…®n aven ghugha, uan tevimning ap…®righa dapanim avira. 
\p  
\v 24 Egha Natan Devit m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúO atrivim, nan gumazir ekiam, n…® ti kamagh…®n m…®keme, Adoniya nan danganim inigh atrivim…®n ik…®va nan atrivir dabirabim dapiam?  
\v 25 E orazi, a dat…®r…®gh…®n ofa damuasa ghua bulmakaun apuriba ko, bulmakaun igiar m…®karziba sara itiba ko, sipsip…®n av…®ribav suegha ofa gami. Egha n…®n otariba ko ofa gamir gumazim Abiatar ko m…®dorozir gumazibar faragha zuir gumazim Joap, a me bagha akaba amangiz…® me ghue. Me dat…®r…®gh…®n dagheba ko d…®paba a koma ada apava an gun tiariba akara ghaze, ‚ÄòAdoniya dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar ruarim…®n atrivim…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äô  
\v 26 Ez…® a, na ko, ofa gamir gumazim Sadok ko, Jehoiadan otarim Benaia ko, n…®n ingangarir gumazim Solomon, an e bagha akatam amadazir puvat…®.  
\v 27 Atrivim, nan Ekiam, manmagh…®ram ami? Me amir bizir kam, n…® an amamangat…®z…® me a gami o? N…® ti, gumazir n…®n danganim inigh, atrivir dabirabim dapiamim, n…® an gun uan ingangarir gumazibav kemezir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 28 Ez…® Atrivim Devit ingangarir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa Batseban diaght…® a ua iz…®.‚Äù Ez…® Batseba ua iza atrivim…®n borogh…®n tu. 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® atrivim a ko akam ak…®ra ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God zurara ikia, egha nan akuragha nan os…®mt…®zir guar av…®ribar aven ua na ini.  
\v 30 An ziam…®n, k…® guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei, dat…®r…®gh…®n aruer kamra, k…® fom…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, an ziam…®n, n…® ko akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamiz…® mogh…®n, k…® a damight…®, an otivam. K…® kamagh…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamua ghaze, n…®n otarim Solomon, nan danganim inigh nan atrivir dabirabim dapiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 31 Ez…® Batseba akar kam baregha, uan tevimning ap…®righa, aviragha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim, n…® nan gumazir ekiam. N…® zurara ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiasa, k…® ifonge.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 32 Ez…® Atrivim Devit kamagh…®n ingangarir gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…®va, ofa gamir gumazim, Sadok ko akam inigha izir gumazim Natan, Jehoiadan otarim Benaia, me m…®kemeght…®, me atrivim…®n guam…®n iz…®.‚Äù Ez…® me aven ize. 
\p  
\v 33 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa nan ingangarir gumaziba inigh mang…®, nan otarim Solomon inigh a is…® nan donki dat…®ght…®, an a daperaght…®, ia a inigh Gihon…®n D…®par Atuir Em…®m…®rim…®n mang…®.  
\v 34 Egh danganir kam…®n, ofa gamir gumazim Sadok, ko akam inigha izir gumazim Natan, Solomon Israelian atrivim…®n otivs…®, aning borem is…® an dapanim gingegh. Ia kamagh…®n damigh g…®vagh, s…®gham givi kamagh…®n araghas…® suam, ‚ÄòAtrivim Solomon dughiar ruarim…®n atrivim…®n ik…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äô  
\v 35 Egh ia an g…®rara iz…®t…®ma, a ua nan d…®penim…®n aven iz…® nan atrivir dabirabim dapiam. K…® Israelia ko Judabar atrivim…®n ikiasa anem…®sefe. Ez…® kamagh…®n, a nan danganim inigh atrivim…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 36 Ez…® Jehoiadan otarim Benaia, kamagh…®n atrivim…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra. Atrivim, n…® nan gumazir ekiam. E kamaghsua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a n…®n God, a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, a bizir kabar amight…® da otivam.  
\v 37 Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…® gamiz…® mogh…®n, a Solomon ko ik…®va an akurvagham. Egh uaghan, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Solomon damight…®, an atrivir gavgavir aghuim…®n otoght…®, an ziar ekiam n…®n ziar ekiam gafiragham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 38 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ofa gamir gumazim Sadok, ko akam inigha izir gumazim Natan, ko Jehoiadan otarim Benaia, ko Keretia, ko Peletian adarasi, me bar ghua Solomon inigha, Atrivim Devit…®n donki gafagha an akua Gihon…®n D…®par Atuir Em…®m…®rim…®n uaghiri.  
\v 39 Ofa gamir gumazim Sadok ghua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim…®n sipsip…®n kom…®n borem aven itim ini. Me Gihon…®n itima, a kom…®n kam inigha borer maba isa Solomon…®n dapanim ginga atrivim…®n otivasa anem…®sefe. Me s…®ghabagh ivima, gumazamiziba bar kamagh…®n araghasi, ‚ÄúSolomon a dughiar ruarim…®n atrivim…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù  
\v 40 Gumazamiziba bar, me bar akongegha diava, marvibagh iviava, Solomon…®n g…®n uamategha Jerusalem…®n zui. Men d…®mdiam bar gavgavigha, nguazim gamima a ivazvasi. 
\s1 Adoniya Atrivim Solomon…®n atiatingi 
\p  
\v 41 Adoniya uan adarazi ko amegha g…®vagha, n…®g…®nir ekiam barasi. Ez…® Joap s…®ghabar ararem baregha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúKar n…®g…®nir ekiar manam Jerusalem…®n oto?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 42 Joap m…®g…®av…®ra itir dughiam…®n, ofa gamir gumazim Abiatar…®n otarim Jonatan, iza me bato. Ez…® Adoniya kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® iz…®. N…® gumazir aghuim, n…® ti akar aghuitam inigha e bagha izi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 43 Ez…® Jonatan kamagh…®n Adoniyan akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúNoki, en gumazir ekiam Atrivim Devit, a Solomon gamiz…®ma an atrivim…®n oto. Kamagh amiz…®, k…® akar aghuitam inigha izir puvat…®.  
\v 44 Atrivim Devit, ofa gamir gumazim Sadok, ko akam inigha izir gumazim Natan ko, Jehoiadan otarim Benaia, ko Keretia, ko Peletian adarasi, bar me amadaz…®, me Solomon ko zui. Me zuir dughiam…®n, me Solomon isa Atrivim Devit…®n donki gis…®n anefaz…®, an aperagha zui.  
\v 45 Me Gihon…®n D…®par Atuir Em…®m…®rim…®n ghua, ofa gamir gumazim Sadok ko akam inigha izir gumazim Natan, aning borem isa Solomon…®n dapanim gingegha, a gamiz…® an atrivim…®n oto. Ez…® kamagh…®n me bar akongegha araghasa uamategha Jerusalem…®n izi, ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Jerusalem…®n itir gumazamiziba bar dia n…®g…®nir dafar kam gami. N…®g…®nir kamra ia dat…®r…®gh…®n a barasi.  
\v 46 Ez…® Solomon dat…®r…®gh…®n atrivim…®n dabirabim gapera.  
\v 47 Ez…® atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazir dapaniba ghua Atrivim Devit…®n gara, uan naviba a gan…®ga kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® dat…®r…®gh…®n bizir bar aghuim gami. Ikiav…®ra Itir God Solomon damight…®, an atrivir gavgavir aghuim…®n otoght…®, an ziar ekiam n…®n ziar ekiam gafiragham.‚Äô Ez…® Atrivim Devit uan dakozim…®n ikia uan dapanim aviragha ziar ekiam God gan…®di.  
\v 48 Egha a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòGod dat…®r…®gh…®n nan otaribar tong…®n mav am…®sevez…®, a nan danganim inigha atrivim…®n iti. God na ataghiz…®, k…® uab…® bizir an amizir kam…®n gari. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, e a bagh, bar akongegham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 49 Gumazir Adoniya koma apiagha ameziba akar kam baregha, me bar atiatigha agoi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me d…®kavigha Adoniya ategha tintinibar ghue.  
\v 50 Ez…® Adoniya, Solomon…®n atiatigha ara ghua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim…®n aven ghua, ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®kebabar itir bulmakaun kombar m…®n garir bizibar suiragha gavgafi.\f + \fr 1:50 \ft Israelia kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gh suam, gumazitam me m…®sueght…® me aremeghs…® damut…®, me ar…® mang…®, God…®n D…®penim…®n aven mang…® ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®kebam…®n itir bulmakaun kom…®n suiragh ikiam. Me kamagh n…®ghn…®si, me an suiragh derav…®ra ikiam. N…® Ua Me Ini 21:13-14…®n gan.\f* 
\v 51 Ez…® gumazir maba ghua Atrivim Solomon m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAdoniya n…®n atiatigha ghua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim…®n aven ghua ovengan atiatigha, ofa gamir dakozim…®n m…®kebabar itir bulmakaun kombar m…®n garir bizibar suiki. Adoniya kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòK…® ofa gamir dakozim…®n suiraghv…®ra ik…® mang…®t…®, Atrivim Solomon, na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeghan koghs…® a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavitam damuam.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 52 Ez…® Solomon kamagh…®n men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúAn arazir aghuim damight…®, bizir kuratam a batoghan kogham. Eght…® an arazir kuram damigh…®va, an ovengam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 53 Egha Atrivim Solomon gumaziba amadaz…®ma, me ghua ofa gamir dakozim…®n Adoniya inigha Solomon bagha ize. Ez…® Adoniya atrivim…®n borogh…®n tevimning ap…®righa aviraz…®, Atrivim Solomon kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uamategh uan d…®penim…®n mang…®.‚Äù 
\c 2  
\s1 Devit akar abuananabar Solomon m…®gei 
\p  
\v 1 Devit fo, an ovengamin dughiam bar rogh…®ra ize, kamagh…®n amiz…®, an akar kaba uan otarim Solomon gan…®di.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Josua 23:14\x*A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® k…®ran oveghang…®n aremegham. N…® guiz…®n gumazim…®n m…®n tugh gavgavigh, uan ingangarim damu.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Josua 1:7; 1 Eghaghaniba 22:12-13\x*N…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God n…® m…®kemezir biziba n…® dar amu. Egh n…® tuavir aghuir an e bagha inabazibar g…®n mang…®, egh arazir a ifongeziba, ko an Akar Gavgaviba, ko bizir a damuasa e m…®kemeziba, ko a m…®geir akaba, n…® bar dar g…®n mang…®. Kamagh…®n God n…®n akuraght…®, danganir manam n…® an iti, n…®n ingangarim bar deraghv…®ram otivam.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt 2 Samuel 7:12-13; 7:25; 2 Atriviba 20:3\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God fom…®ra akar d…®k…®r…®zir mam…®n na gamigha ghaze, ‚ÄòDevit, n…®n ovavir boriba zurara uan navir averiaba ko duabar, bar derav…®ra nan damazim…®n daru mang…®t…®, k…® zurara n…®n adarazir gumazitam damight…®, a Israelian atrivim…®n otivam.‚Äô Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Solomon, n…® guizbang…®ra bar deraghv…®ra an akabar g…®n mang…®, eght…® a na gamizir akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam abighan kogham. 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt 2 Samuel 3:27; 20:10\x*‚ÄúEz…® Solomon, n…® oragh. N…® fogha g…®fa, Seruian otarim Joap, an arazir kurar kam, an os…®mt…®zir ekiam na gan…®ngi. A Israelian m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanir faragha zuimning m…®soghez…®, aning areme. Kar, Ner…®n otarim Apner ko Jeter…®n otarim Amasa. A m…®dorozim…®n dughiam…®n aning m…®soghez…® aning aremezir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. A pura gumazir kamning m…®soghez…® aning areme, ez…® aning…®n os…®mt…®zim an ikiav…®ra iti.  
\v 6 N…® uan n…®ghn…®zir aghuim…®n g…®n mang…®va, an arazir kuram uam a ikaragh. N…® aneteght…® a pura ik…® ghurigh uab…® aremegh Gumazamizir Oveaghuezibar Nguibam…®n mag…®ran mark…®. 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt 2 Samuel 17:27-29\x*‚ÄúN…® uaghan Barsilain otaribar apangkuvigh deraghv…®ra me damu, kar Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n gumazim, n…® me ateght…® me iz…® n…®n adarazi ko dapiagh dam…® ik…®. K…® fom…®ra n…®n aveghbuam Apsalom…®n aravghuzir dughiam…®n, me arazir aghuim…®n na gami. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt 2 Samuel 16:5-13; 19:16-23\x*‚ÄúEz…® Geran otarim Simei, a Bahurim…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazim, a Benjamin…®n anabam…®n mav, a uaghan iti. K…® t…®ghar Mahanaim…®n mangamin dughiam…®n, aruer kamra a bar akar kuraba na gan…®ga, egha na gas…®ghas…®ghasa God…®n azangs…®si. Egha a ua iza Jordan…®n Fanem…®n na batoz…®ma, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamua ghaze, k…® a m…®sueght…® an aremeghan kogham.  
