\v 31 Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n Benaian akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúA dera, n…® an n…®ghn…®zim…®n g…®n mang…®va a m…®sueght…®, an aremegh. Egh an kuam inigh mang…® anefagh. Joap gumazir os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®ziba pura me m…®soaghar…®ghiz…® me ariaghire. Ez…® an os…®mt…®zir kam, na ko nan afeziam…®n adarazir iti. N…® a m…®sueght…®, an aremeght…®, an os…®mt…®zir kam uam en ikian kogham.  
\v 32 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Joap amizir arazir kurar kaba ikarvagh, ivezir kuram a dan…®ngam. Joap Ner…®n otarim Apner ko Jeter…®n otarim Amasa, a m…®dorozir sabam…®n puram aning m…®soghez…® aning areme. Aning an m…®n gumazir kuramning puvat…®. Apner, a Israelian m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim, ez…® Amasa, a Judabar m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim. Nan afeziam Devit fozir puvat…®z…®, Joap arazir kam gami.  
\v 33 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Joap amizir os…®mt…®zir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, zurara m…®zazim Joap ko an adarazir an…®ngam. Egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, zurara dabirabir aghuim ko navir am…®rizim is…®, Devit ko an ovavir boriba, ko an adarasi, ko an ik…®zim…®n otivamin atrivibar an…®ngam.‚Äù 
