\v 36 Joap aremegha g…®vaz…®ma, Atrivim Solomon Simein diagha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Jerusalem…®n d…®penitam…®n ingarigh, egh d…®penir kamra ik…®. Egh n…® bar Jerusalem ategh igharagh mangan mark…®.  
