\v 4 Nguibar ekiam Gibeon, a m…®ghs…®am…®n p…®n ikia egha ofa gamir danganir ekiam iti, egha ofa gamir danganir igharazibagh afira. Ez…® me kagh ghuegha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dughiar kam…®n Solomon ofa damuasa Gibeon…®n ghu. Solomon 1,000plan as…®ziba inigha ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba tuasa Gibeon…®n ofan dakozir kam…®n ghua da tue.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt 1 Atriviba 9:2; 2 Eghaghaniba 1:7\x*D…®magarir mam, Solomon Gibeon…®n nguibam…®n ikia akua irebam…®n garima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uab…® an akagha a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® bizir tizim gifongegh, nan azaraght…®, k…® n…® dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
