\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 1:10; Aghuzir Akaba 2:3-9; Hibru 5:14; Jems 1:5\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ko fofozim na danight…®, k…® deraghv…®ra n…®n gumazamizibagh ativagh men ganam. Egh k…® fogham, arazir manam a dera, manam ikufi. Puvat…®ght…®, k…® manmagh…®ra n…®n gumazamizir av…®rir kam gativagh men ganam? Guizbang…®ra, gumazitam uab…® me gativan iburagham. K…® uab…® k…® fofoziba bar puvat…®.‚Äù 
