\v 11 Egha God Solomon m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® dughiar ruarim…®n nguazir kam…®n ikiasa, nan azangs…®zir puvat…®, egha dag…®ar av…®riba iniasa nan azai puvat…®, egha uan apanibagh as…®ghas…®ghasa nan azai puvat…®. N…® Israelia gativagh deraghv…®ra men ganamin n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ko fofozim iniasa nan azai.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt 1 Atriviba 4:29-31; Fofozir Gumazim 1:16\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® guizbang…®ra, bizir n…® uab…® dan…®ngasa nan azangs…®zim, k…® a is…® n…® dan…®ngam. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ko fofozir aghuim n…® dan…®ngam. Gumazitam fom…®ra fofozir kamagh garitam itir puvat…®, egh uaghan g…®n gumazitam fofozir kamagh garitam ikian kogham.  
\v 13 Guizbang…®ra, n…® ziar ekiam ko dag…®ar av…®riba uab…® dan…®ngasa nan azarazir puvat…®. Ez…® k…® bizir kaba bar n…® dan…®ngam. Dughiar n…® atrivim…®n ikiamim, atrivir igharazitam n…® itir ziar ekiar kam itir puvat…®.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt 1 Atriviba 15:5; Onger Akaba 91:16; Aghuzir Akaba 3:2\x*Egh n…® uan afeziam Devit…®n m…®n nan tuaviba ko arazir k…® ifongeziba ko nan Akar Gavgavibar g…®n mang…®t…®, k…® n…® damut…® n…® dughiar ruarim…®n nguazir kam…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
