\v 27 \x - \xo 8:27 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 2:6; Aisaia 66:1; Aposel 7:49; 17:24\x*‚ÄúO God, guizbang…®ra n…® ti iz…® nguazir kam…®n ikiam o? E fo, overiar bar p…®n itim a bar ekefe, ez…® n…® an ikiamin danganiba ti puvat…®ghama! Eght…® d…®penir k…® n…® bagha ingarizir kam, a manmagh…®n n…®n tughat…®gham?  
\v 28 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan God, k…® n…®n ingangarir gumazim, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n nan ararem ko azangs…®zim barakigh.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 8:29 \xt God…®n Araziba 12:11\x*N…® kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòD…®penir kam kar n…®na, eght…® gumazamiziba an aven iz…®va n…®n borogh…®n izam.‚Äô K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, N…® arueba ko d…®magaribar zurara damazim D…®penir kam gasaragh mamagh…®ra ik…®. Eght…® k…® D…®penir kam…®n gan…®va n…® ko m…®k…®mamin dughiabar, n…® nan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baragh.  
\v 30 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® uan Nguibam…®n p…®n iti. K…® Israelia ko, e n…®n gumazamiziba e n…®n D…®penim…®n gan…®va n…® ko m…®k…®mamin dughiabar, n…® en m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baragh en arazir kuraba g…®n amang. 
\p  
\v 31 ‚ÄúGumazitam, arazir kuratam gumazir igharazitam damight…®, an namakaba a inigh n…®n D…®penim…®n aven iz…®, egh n…®n ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n mang…®, egh paz…® gumazir kam damus…® n…®n azangam.  
\v 32 \x - \xo 8:32 \xt God…®n Araziba 25:1\x*O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® uan nguibam…®n ik…®, uan ingangarir gumazamizibar akaba baragh, deraghv…®ra men kotiam ak…®righ. Egh n…® m…®zazim is…® gumazir os…®mt…®zim gamizim gas…®, egh os…®mt…®zir kuram…®n uam a ikaragh. Egh n…® deraghv…®ra os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®zir gumazim damight…®, gumazamiziba bizir kam…®n ganigh fogh suam an arazir kuram gamizir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 33 \x - \xo 8:33-39 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 7:12-20\x*‚ÄúE Israelia, n…®n gumazamiziba e arazir kurabar amut…®, bizir kam bang…®n en apaniba e m…®soght…®, n…® apanibar amamangat…®ght…® me e ab…®ragham. Eght…® e ti ua uan navibagh iragh, uan arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®s…®, n…®n D…®penim…®n iz…® n…®n ziam f…® n…®n azangs…®ght…®,  
\v 34 n…® uan Nguibam…®n ik…® e Israelia n…®n gumazamiziba en azangs…®ziba baragh, en arazir kuraba g…®n amang. Egh en apaniba e inigh kantrin igharazim…®n mang…®ght…®, n…® uam e inigh iz…® kantrin n…® fom…®ra en inazir afeziabagh an…®ngizim…®n e at…®gh. 
\p  
\v 35 ‚ÄúEght…® e n…®n gumazamiziba arazir kurabar amut…®, n…® en arazir kuraba ikarvagh amozim…®n anogoregham. Eght…®, e uan navibagh iragh D…®penir kam…®n gan n…®n ziam f…®, n…®n azangs…®ght…®,  
\v 36 n…® uan Nguibam…®n ik…®, e Israelia, n…®n ingangarir gumazamiziba, en azangs…®ziba baragh, en arazir kuraba g…®n amang. Egh n…® uan arazir aghuibar en sure damu. Egh amozim amadaght…® a nguazir n…® fom…®ra e gan…®ngizim gir…®. 
\p  
\v 37 ‚ÄúEght…® dagheba otevir dughiam en kantri batogham, o ar…®mariar kurar ekiatam otogham, o am…®nir avim…®n m…®n isitam iz…® azenibagh as…®ghasigham, o azenibar itir dagheba pura kuram, o odezir av…®riba daghebar am…® da ag…®vam, o apaniba iz…® en nguibar ekiabar e korogh e m…®sogham, o ar…®mariar igharagha garir av…®riba e gas…®ghas…®gham,  
\v 38 bizir kaba otivt…®, e Israelia n…®n gumazamiziba, en tav os…®mt…®zir kabar tam…®n m…®zazim baragh, uan aghariba fegh n…®n azangs…®ght…®,  
\v 39 \x - \xo 8:39 \xt 1 Samuel 16:7; Onger Akaba 11:4; Aposel 1:24\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® uan Nguibam…®n ik…®va en azangs…®zim baregh en akuragh, en arazir kuraba g…®n amadagh. N…®rara gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®ziba bar dagh fo, kamagh…®n, n…® uab…® vaghvagh en arazir kurar e amiziba ikarvagh ivezir kuram e dan…®ng.  
\v 40 N…® kamagh…®n damight…®ma, e n…®n gumazamiziba zurara n…®n apengan ik…®, egh nguazir n…® en inazir afeziabagh an…®ngizir kam…®n ikiam. 
\p  
\v 41-42 ‚ÄúKantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, me n…®n adarazi Israelian aven itir puvat…®, egh me n…®n ziam bang…®n, uan nguibar saghon itiba ategh kagh izam. Guizbang…®ra, me n…®n ziar ekiam ko, ingangarir bar ekiar n…® en gumazamizibar akurvaghasa amiziba, me da baraki. Egh men tarazi, n…®n ziam f…®s…®, n…®n D…®penir kam…®n borogh…®ra iz…®, egh n…® ko m…®k…®mam.  
\v 43 \x - \xo 8:43 \xt 1 Samuel 17:46; 2 Atriviba 19:19; Onger Akaba 67:2\x*O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® uan Nguibam…®n iti, egh n…® men d…®mdiam baragh, egh bizir me damuasa n…®n azangs…®zibar amu. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e Israelia, n…®n gumazamiziba, e ami mogh…®n, nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar n…® g…®fogh egh n…®n atiating n…®n apengan ikiam. Egh me fogh suam, D…®penir k…® ingarizir kam, kar n…®n D…®penimra, eght…® an aven nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba me n…®n borogh…®ra izam. 
\p  
\v 44 ‚ÄúEgh danganir manam…®n n…® uan gumazamiziba amadaght…®, me mang…® uan apanibav soghs…®, n…®n nguibar ekiar n…® ua bagha m…®sevezir kam ko D…®penir k…® n…® bagha ingarizir kam, guam a m…®tuagh n…® ko m…®k…®mt…®,  
\v 45 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® uan Nguibam…®n ik…®, e uarir akurvaghasa n…® ko m…®geir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baragh en apangkufigh. 
\p  
\v 46 ‚ÄúGumazamiziba bar mogh…®ram arazir kurabagh ami. Eght…® e arazir kurabar amight…® n…® en atar en apanibar amamangat…®ght…®, me iz…® e ko m…®sogh e ab…®nigh e inigh mang…®, kantrin saghon itim o rogh…®ra itim…®n e is…® kalabuziabar m…®n e ar…®gham.  
\v 47-49 Eght…® e men kantrin kam…®n aven kalabuziar gumazamizibar m…®n ik…®va, uan arazir kuraba bagh n…®ghn…®gh navibagh iraght…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® e uarir akurvaghamin azangs…®ziba baragh. Guizbang…®ra, e uan apanibar kantrin ik…®va n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim n…®n ik…®, uan navir averiabar aven n…® baghv…®ra ik…® guizbang…®ra navibagh iragh, egh e nguazir n…® en ovavibagh an…®ngizir kam ko, nguibar ekiar n…® ua baghav…®ra inabazir kam ko, gumazamiziba n…® bagh izamin D…®penir k…® n…® bagha ingarizir kam…®n gan…®va guam a m…®tuagh kamagh…®n n…® ko m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòE arazir kurabar tuavim…®n ghua arazir kurar av…®ribagh amigha g…®fa.‚Äô Eght…® n…® uan Nguibam…®n ik…®, e n…® ko m…®geir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baragh, e n…®n gumazamiziba, n…® en kuarkuvigh en akuragh, en arazir kuraba g…®n amadagh.  
\v 50 Egh e n…®n gumazamiziba, en n…®n akaba batozir arazim ko, en arazir kurar av…®rir e amiba, n…® da g…®n amadagh, egh en apanibar amight…® me en kuarkufigh.  
\v 51 E Israelia guiz…®n n…®n gumazamiziba. N…® Isip…®n kantrin e inigha azenan ize, kantrin kam avir fefer ekiar mam…®n m…®n iti, ez…® n…® an e inigha ize. 
\p  
\v 52 ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, e n…®n gumazamiziba ko en atrivim, a n…®n ingangarir gumazim, e n…® ko m…®geir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba n…® zurara da baraghs…® oragh ik…®.  
\v 53 N…® akam ak…®rizim mogh…®n, e Israelia, n…® kantrin igharazibar tong…®n e am…®sevez…® e n…®n gumazamizibar otifi. O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® en Ekiam, n…® en inazir afeziaba Isip…®n me inigha izir dughiam…®n, n…® uan ingangarir gumazim Moses, an akatorim…®n aven, n…® akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam gami.‚Äù 
\s1 God deragh gumazamizibar amuasa, Solomon an azangs…®si 
\p  
\v 54 Solomon Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®k…®masa, ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n tevimning ap…®righa agharimning fuegha a ko m…®gei. Egha an a ko m…®kemegha g…®fa.  
\v 55 Egha Solomon d…®kavigha tugha gumazamizibar damazim…®n tiarir ekiam…®n, God deragh Israelia damuasa a ko m…®gei.  
\v 56 \x - \xo 8:56 \xt God…®n Araziba 12:10; Josua 21:44-45; 23:14; 1 Atriviba 2:4\x*A ghaze, ‚ÄúE Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fam, a uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim…®n g…®n ghua, navir am…®rizim ko dabirabir aghuim isa Israelia gan…®ngi. A uan ingangarir gumazim Moses ko d…®k…®r…®zir akatam, pura ghuzir puvat…®.  
\v 57 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a en God, a faragha en inazir afeziaba ko ikez…® mogh…®n, dat…®r…®gh…®n an e ko ikiam. An e ateght…®, e pura uarira ikian kogham.  
\v 58 An e damut…® en naviba a baghv…®ra ik…®, egh an Akar Gavgaviba, ko an arazir a ifongeziba ko, bizir a damuasa en inazir afeziabav kemeziba, e derav…®ra dar g…®n mangam.  
\v 59 K…® God ko m…®geir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, ko bizir k…® damuasava an azangs…®ziba, an ada is…® bar uan n…®ghn…®zim dar…®gham. A uaghan, Israelia uan atrivim ko, apangkuvim men ik…® men akurvagh, dughiabar vaghvagh men akurvaght…®, me dagheba ko bizibar oteveghan kogham.  
\v 60 Eght…® nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar fogh suam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a God, ez…® god…®n tam ua itir puvat…®.  
\v 61 Ia bar mogh…®ra uari is…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God dan…®ng, egh an Akar Gavgaviba ko an arazir a ifongeziba, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n ami mogh…®n deraghv…®ra dar g…®n mang…®.‚Äù 
\s1 D…®penir kam, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God baghav…®rama a ginaba 
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 7:4-10) 
\p  
\v 62 Egha Atrivim Solomon uan gumazamiziba ko me bar mogh…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ofabagh ami.  
\v 63 Solomon God ko navir vam…®ran ikiasa 22,000plan bulmakaun apuriba ko 120,000plan sipsipba inigha ofa gami. Arazir kam…®n atrivim uan gumazamiziba ko me D…®penir kam gamiz…®ma, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n oto.  
\v 64 Aruer kamra atrivim nguazir God…®n D…®penim…®n guam…®n borogh…®n itir danganir uari akuvim, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha anem…®sevez…®, an a baghav…®ra iti. Egha nguazir as…®zir kam…®n, an ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba ko, wit tuamin ofaba ko, God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofa bagha as…®zibar oviba isa ofabagh ami. Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n tughav itir ofa gamir dakozir kam, me faragha bras…®n an ingariz…®, a mong suviz…® me an ofan av…®rir kabar amuan iburagha, danganir arozir gumazamiziba uari akuvir kam…®n ofabagh ami. 
\p  
\v 65 Kar Averpenibar Ikiamin Dughiar Ekiam. Ez…® Atrivim Solomon Israelia ko uari akuvagha Jerusalem…®n iti. Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God…®n damazim…®n, 7plan aruebar uari akuvagha ikegha, g…®n me ua 7plan arueba isafuragha 14plan arueba me bar dar ike. Gumazamizir av…®rim nguazir kam…®n danganiba bar dar ikegha ize. Not…®n amadaghan Hamat…®n nguibar ekiam…®n zuir tuavir akam…®n ikegha, ghua saut…®n amadaghan kantri Isip…®n nguazir m…®taghniam…®n tu.  
\v 66 Aruer ekiar kaba g…®vaz…®ma, am…®mzaraghan Solomon gumazamiziba ua me amadima, me uamategha uan nguibabar zui. Egha gumazamiziba atrivim me gan…®ngizir biziba bagha a m…®nabagha, God deragh atrivim damuasa me an azai. Me fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan ingangarir gumazim Devit ko, d…®k…®r…®zir akam…®n g…®n ghua, uan gumazamiziba Israelia deraghav…®ra me gami. Egha me uamategha ghua, bizir aghuir kabagh n…®ghn…®gha bar akongegha uan nguibabar zui. 
\c 9  
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ua Solomon bato 
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 7:11-22) 
\p  
\v 1 Solomon Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ko, atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n ingarigha g…®fa. A d…®penir kamning…®n ingaramin n…®ghn…®ziba, a bar ada g…®fa.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 9:2 \xt 1 Atriviba 3:5; 2 Eghaghaniba 1:7\x*Ez…® g…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God faragha Gibeon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n irebam…®n a batoz…® mogh…®n, uam a bato.  
\v 3 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® n…®n azangs…®ziba baregha g…®fa. Egha n…® ingarizir D…®penir kam ua bagha a ginabagha g…®fa, eght…® gumazamiziba zurara dughiabar D…®penir kam…®n aven iz…®va nan borogh…®n izam. Eght…® k…® zurara D…®penir kam damazim a gas…®, egh uan navir averiam…®n aven a g…®n…®ghn…®gham.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 9:4 \xt 1 Atriviba 3:14; 11:4-6\x*Eght…® n…® uan afeziam Devit amiz…® mogh…®n, n…® navir averiam…®n aven na baghv…®ra n…®ghn…®gh nan damazim…®n derav…®ra daru, egh arazir k…® ifongeziba ko bizir k…® damuasa ia m…®kemeziba, k…® n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n bizibar amu.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 9:5 \xt 1 Atriviba 2:4\x*N…® kamagh…®n damut…®, k…® zurara n…®n ovavir boribar amut…®, me Israel…®n atrivibar ik…® mang…®v…®ra ikiam. Egh k…® n…®n afeziam Devit ko amizir akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam damight…®, a guiz…®n otivam. K…® kamagh…®n Devit m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòDevit, k…® zurara n…®n ovavir boribar amut…®, me Israelian atrivibar ik…® mang…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äô 
\p  
\v 6 ‚ÄúEgh Solomon, n…® uan ovavir borir g…®n otivamiba ko, ia na ategh nan Akar Gavgaviba ko arazir k…® ifongezibar g…®n mangan kogh, egh asebar g…®n mang…® dar ziaba f…®t…®,  
\v 7 k…® nguazir Israelia ia gan…®ngizim…®n bar ia batuegham. Eght…® ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamiziba d…®bovir akabar ia m…®k…®m ian ziam gas…®ghas…®gham. K…® uaghan, ak…®rim ragh D…®penir k…® ua bagha inabazim gasaragham, egh uam a g…®n…®ghn…®ghan kogham.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 9:8 \xt 2 Atriviba 25:9; 2 Eghaghaniba 36:19\x*D…®penir kam, dat…®r…®gh…®n ziar ekiam iti. Eght…® g…®n gumazir danganir kam…®n izamiba me iz…®va an gan me d…®pov ak…® m…®soribar an…®ng, d…®gavir kuram damigh, egh bar atiatigh, kamagh…®n m…®k…®mam, ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, manmaghsuav…®ra nguazir kam gas…®ghas…®gha, egha D…®penir kam sarama as…®ghas…®ki?‚Äô  
\v 9 Eght…® gumazitaba men akam ikaragh suam, ‚ÄòBizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, Israelia Ikiav…®ra Itir God men God, anetaki. A fom…®ra men inazir afeziaba Isip…®n me inigha nguzir kam…®n ize. Ez…® me God ategha, ragha uan asebar g…®n ghua dar ziaba fe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God as…®ghas…®zir kam gamiz…®ma a me bato.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\s1 Solomon bizir aghuir mam isa  // Atrivim Hiram gan…®ngi 
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 8:1-2) 
\p  
\v 10 Solomon uan ingangarir gumaziba ko, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ingara aneg…®vagha, egha g…®n me Solomon…®n d…®penim…®n ingari. Ingangarir me amir kaba bar, me 20plan azenibar dar ingari.  
\v 11 Tair…®n nguibar ekiam…®n Atrivim Hiram, Solomon ifongez…® mogh…®n, sidan temeba ko pain…®n temeba ko gol…®n av…®riba, ingangarir kabar amuasa Solomon gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ingangarir kaba bar g…®vaz…®, Solomon 20plan nguibar ekiaba bizir aghuim…®n m…®n da isa Hiram gan…®ngi. Nguibar ekiar kaba da Galilin Distrigh…®n iti.  
\v 12 Ez…® Hiram Tair…®n nguibar ekiam ategha iza Solomon a gan…®ngizir nguibar ekiar kabar ganigha, dagh ifongezir puvat…®.  
\v 13 Egha a kamagh…®n Solomon m…®gei, ‚ÄúNan aveghbuam, kar manmagh garir nguibar ekiaba, n…® da isa na gan…®ngi?‚Äù Bizir kam bagha, dat…®r…®gh…®n gumazamiziba danganir kam ziar kam a gar…®si, ‚ÄúKabul.‚Äù\f + \fr 9:13 \ft Hibrun akam…®n ziar kam, ‚ÄúKabul,‚Äù a mong akar kam ko vorogh…®ra ghu, ‚ÄúNguazir ikuvim.‚Äù\f* 
\v 14 Hiram faragha gol…®n bar av…®rim isa Solomon gan…®ngi, ez…® dar os…®mt…®zim 4pla tan…®n tu. 
\s1 Solomon amizir bizir igharaziba 
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 8:3-18) 
\p  
\v 15 \x - \xo 9:15 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 8:16\x*Atrivim Solomon gumazir bar av…®rim inigha me m…®g…®a ghaze, me an ingangaribar amuam. A me m…®geima, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ingarigha uaghan an d…®penim sara ingarigha, d…®vazir ekiar Jerusalem av…®nizim…®n ingari. Egha me m…®kemez…®, me Jerusalem…®n nguazibagh kua da isa Jerusalem…®n danganir iraghuezibav k…®ra da apeme. Egha me m…®kemez…®, me nguibar ekiar kaba uam adar k…®ri, Hasor, Megido ko Geser.  
\v 16 Geser…®n nguibar ekiam, a fom…®ra Kenanian nguibar ekiam, ez…® Isipian atrivim iza me m…®soghez…® me ariaghirez…® me a gaboroz…® a isi. Ez…® Solomon Isip…®n atrivim…®n guivim inigha an itima, atrivim Geser…®n nguibar ekiar kam bizir aghuim…®n m…®n a isa uan guivim gan…®ngi.  
\v 17 Ez…® Solomon g…®n ua Geser…®n nguibar ekiar kam…®n ingari. A g…®n Bethoron…®n nguibar ekiar v…®n amadaghan itim ko,  
\v 18 Balat ko Tamar…®n nguibamning…®n ingari. Tamar…®n nguibar ekiam, Judan anabam…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n iti.  
\v 19 Egha a uaghan dagheba itir nguibar ekiaba ko m…®dorozir karisba ar…®zir nguibar ekiaba ko, hoziaba ar…®zir nguibar ekiaba ko, Jerusalem ko, Lebanon ko, nguazir an ativagha garibar aven, a bizir igharazir a ingarasa ifongeziba, bar adar ingari. 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® Israel…®n kantrin aven, ik…®zir igharazir mabar gumazamiziba iti. Kar Amoria, Hitia, Peresia, Hivia, ko Jebusia, men marazi Israelian tong…®n ikiav…®ra iti.  
\v 21 Israelia fom…®ra men av…®ribav soghez…® me ariaghire, egha bar me kuavaremezir puvat…®z…®, men ovavir borir vabara ikiav…®ra iti. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Solomon me gamiz…®ma, me puram an ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar m…®n otivigha, dat…®r…®gh…®n ikia kamagh…®ra iti.\f + \fr 9:21 \ft M…®g…®r…®g…®ar otevir kam, ‚Äúdat…®r…®gh…®n uaghan,‚Äù an en itir dughiar kam m…®geir puvat…®. A gumazir ak…®nafarir kam osirizim…®n dughiam m…®gei.\f* 
\v 22 Ez…® Israelia, Solomon me gamiz…® me an ingangarir gumazir k…®nibar itir pu. Bar puvat…®, a me isa m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, gavman…®n ingangarim gamir gumazir dapaniba, ko m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir dapanibar me ar…®ki. Egha marazi isa, karis…®n tuiva ghua m…®sozir ingangarim ko, gumazir hoziabagh apiagha ghua m…®sozibar ingangarim me gan…®ngi.  
\v 23 Solomon…®n ingangaribagh amir gumaziba, men garir gumazir dapanibar d…®bobonim, a 550…®n tu. 
\p  
\v 24 Solomon…®n amuim, a Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam ategha ghua Solomon a bagha ingarizir d…®penir igiam…®n iti. Amizir kam, a Isipian atrivim…®n guivim. Egha g…®n, Solomon gumazibav m…®kemez…®, me Jerusalem…®n itir danganir iraghueziba apeme. 
\p  
\v 25 \x - \xo 9:25 \xt Ua Me Ini 23:17; 34:23; God…®n Araziba 16:16\x*Egha azeniba vaghvagha, Solomon 3plan dughiabar ingarizir ofan dakozir kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ofa bagh ami. A ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba ko, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofaba tue. Egha a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ofan m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuibagh ami. Kamagh…®ra, Solomon ofan kabagh amua D…®penir kam…®n ingangarim gamiz…®, a guizbang…®rama oto.\f + \fr 9:25 \ft Hibrun akam, deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\p  
\v 26 Atrivim Solomon, a Esiongeber…®n nguibar ekiam…®n kurir av…®ribar ingari. Esiongeber a kantri Idom…®n iti, an Ongarir Aghevim…®n dadarim…®n ikia Elat…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n iti.  
\v 27 Ez…® Atrivim Hiram uan gumazir aghuir kuribar aven ingara ongarim…®n aruir arazim…®n bar a g…®foziba amadaz…®, me ghua Solomon…®n kuribar aven ingarir gumaziba ko me kurir kabar aven ingari.  
\v 28 Ez…® kurir kaba kantri Ofir…®n ghua gol…®n av…®riba isa Solomon bagha izi. Gol…®n kabar os…®mt…®zim 14plan tanbagh afira. 
\c 10  
\s1 Seban kantrin atrivir amizim Solomon…®n ganasa izi 
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 9:1-12) 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 10:1-10 \xt Matyu 12:42; Luk 11:31\x*Kantri Seban atrivir amizim kamagh…®n oraki, Ikiav…®ra Itir God deraghav…®ra Solomon gamiz…®ma a ziar ekiam iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, atrivir amizim Solomon…®n fofozim g…®fofoghasa azangs…®zir gavgavibar an azangs…®ghasa izi.  
\v 2 Atrivir amizim uan ingangarir gumazir av…®riba ko, kamel…®n b…®zir av…®riba sara iza Jerusalem…®n oto. Kamel…®n kaba gol…®n av…®riba ko, pauran igharagha garir mughuriar aghuiba itiba, ko dag…®ar igharagha garir iveziba bar p…®n koziba inigha izi. Atrivir amizim izegha g…®vagha, uan azangs…®zir a Solomon…®n azangs…®ghasa n…®ghn…®ghiziba, a bar dar an azangs…®si.  
\v 3 Ez…® Solomon bar deraghav…®ra an azangs…®ziba ikarvaki. An azangs…®zir an azangs…®ziba, Solomon tam ikarvaghan iburazir pu. Bar puvat…®.  
\v 4 Seban kantrin atrivir amizim, Solomon…®n n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ko fofozim baraki, egha a uaghan atrivibar d…®penir ekiar a ingarizim…®n gani.  
\v 5 Egha atrivir amizim uaghan garima, Solomon dughiabar vaghvagha dagher aghuir av…®riba isa, uan ingangarir gumazir dapaniba ko apiav ikia da api. Ez…® atrivir amizim uaghan garima, ingangarir gumaziba ko men korotiar aghuir me azuiba ko gumazir wain an…®diba, me kurkazir aghuiba iti. Egha a garima, Solomon as…®zir av…®riba inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ghua a bagha ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribagh ami. A bizir aghuir kabar ganigha d…®gavir kuram gamigha ua m…®k…®man ibura. 
\p  
\v 6 Egha g…®n, a kamagh…®n Atrivim Solomon m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® uan kantrin ikiava bizir n…® amibar eghaghaniba ko, n…®n n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ko, fofozim barasi. Ez…® k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, akar kaba da bar guizbang…®ra.  
\v 7 K…® faragha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim akar kabar itir puvat…®. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® uab…® iza, uan damazim…®n bizir kabar ganigha g…®fa. Guizbang…®ra, bizir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n gariba, da akar k…® oraghiziba bar dagh afira. N…®n n…®ghn…®zir aghuim ko fofozir aghuim bar ekevez…®, n…®n dag…®aba bar av…®raseme.  
\v 8 N…®n gumazamiziba ti zurara bar akueghama. Ez…® n…®n ingangaribar faragha zuir gumazir n…® ko ikia zurara n…®n n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba baraziba, me ti bar akueghama.  
\v 9 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God…®n ziam fe. A navir aghuim n…®n ikia n…® gamiz…®, n…® Israelian atrivim…®n iti. A bar Israelia ia gifongegha, an ifongiar kam ian ikiav…®ra iti. N…® guiz…®n arazim ko arazir aghuim…®n deraghv…®ra Israelian gan me geghuvam. A kamaghsua n…® gamiz…®, n…® atrivim…®n oto.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Egha Seban atrivir amizim gol…®n bar av…®riba isa Solomon gan…®ngi, ez…® gol…®n kabar os…®mt…®zim 4 tan gafira. Atrivir amizim uaghan pauran mughuriar aghuiba itir av…®riba ko, dag…®ar igharagha garir iveziba bar p…®n kozir av…®riba a gan…®ngi. Bar guizbang…®ra, bizir kaba bar av…®raseme. Dughiar kam…®n g…®n, pauran av…®rir igharagha garitaba ua kantri Israel…®n aven izezir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Atrivim Hiram…®n ingangarir gumaziba, an kuriba ghua kantri Ofir…®n ghua gol…®n av…®riba ko, temer aghuibar b…®ghizir arariba ko, dag…®ar av…®rir iveziba bar p…®n koziba, me da inigha Israel…®n ize.  
\v 12 Ez…® Solomon uan ingangarir gumazibav m…®kemez…®, me temer aghuir kaba inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim bagh ad…®r…®ziar aghuibagh amua an d…®penim bagha mabagh ami. Egha a me m…®kemez…®, me temer aghuir kabar arariba inigha gumazir gitabav soziba bagha gitabar ingari. Bar fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, gumaziba kantri Israel…®n aven, ua temer kamagh garitabar garir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Atrivim Solomon, bizir aghuir av…®riba isa Seban atrivir amizim…®n ifongiam ag…®vasa a gan…®ngi. Solomon atrivir amizim gan…®ngizir bizir av…®riba, da bar bizir atrivir amizim Solomon bagha inigha izezir bizibagh afira. Ez…® Seban atrivir amizim, uan ingangarir gumaziba ko me uamategha uan kantrin ghu. 
\s1 Solomon dag…®ar av…®riba iti 
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 9:13-28) 
\p  
\v 14 Solomon azenibar vaghvagha 23 tan gol isi.  
\v 15 Egha a uaghan dag…®ar ingangaribagh amir gumaziba da takis isi. Ez…® Arebian atriviba ko, Israel…®n distrighbar garir gumazir dapaniba dag…®aba isa a gan…®di. 
\p  
\v 16 Solomon m…®kemez…®ma, an ingangarir gumaziba 200plan ter araribar orar m…®soghamibar ingari. Egha me gol inigha orar kabar pogha da ave. Orar kaba vaghvagha da avezir gol…®n os…®mt…®zim, a 7 kilogrem…®n tu.  
\v 17 Egha 300plan ter araribar orar dozir m…®soghamiba uaghan dar ingari. Egha gol inigha orar dozir kabar pogha da ave. Orar kaba vaghvagha da avezir gol…®n os…®mt…®zim, a 2 kilogrem…®n tu. Ez…® Solomon m…®kemez…®ma, me orar kaba bar da inigha d…®penir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n da ar…®ki, Lebanon…®n Ruarir P…®zim…®n D…®penim. 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® Solomon m…®kemez…®, me atrivir dabirabir ekiar mam…®n ingari. Egha me gol…®n aghuim ko, elefan…®n atariba inigha an kurke.  
\v 19-20 Atrivim…®n dabirabim bar p…®n iti, ez…® ad…®r…®ziar tuiv mavanangamim, a 6plan ighuviba iti. Ez…® ighuvir kaba, me 12plan laion…®n nedazibar ingarigha da asez…® da tuivighav iti. Ez…® ad…®r…®ziar ighuvir kaba vaghvagha laion…®n nedazir pumuning iti, mam vong…®n iti, ez…® mam vong…®n iti. Ez…® atrivim…®n dabirabir kam…®n g…®rak…®rang…®n, vong…®n ghuavanabogha ik…®ragha ua vong…®n izaghir…®. Atrivir dabirabir kam, an agharimning ar…®ghamin danganir pumuning iti. Ez…® agharimning ar…®ghamin danganir kamning…®n borogh…®n, me laion…®n nedazir pumuning…®n ingariz…®, aning vong ko vong sara iti. Kantrin igharazibar atriviba, men atrivibar dabirabitam tong kamagh…®n garir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® ingangarir gumaziba gol inigha Solomon bagha d…®paba apir itaribar ingari. Egha Lebanon…®n Ruarir P…®zim…®n D…®penim…®n aven itir itariba bar, me gol…®n aghuim…®n dar ingari. Solomon…®n dughiam…®n, gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®zim, silva pura bizim, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me silvan bizir katam…®n ingarizir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 22 Solomon kurir av…®riba iti, ez…® kurir kaba da Atrivim Hiram…®n kuriba ko, ongarim…®n arui. Kurir kaba zurara azenir 3pla g…®vaght…®, me bizir aghuir kaba ater ua Israel…®n izam. Kar gol, ko silva, ko elefan…®n atariba, ko monkiba, ko kuarazir bar diriba. 
\p  
\v 23 Atrivim Solomon, dag…®ar av…®riba ko bizir av…®riba ko n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ko fofozir aghuiba ikia, egha kantrin igharazibar atriviba bar me gafira.  
\v 24 Kantrin igharazibar atriviba bar, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Solomon gan…®ngizir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ko, fofozir aghuiba baraghasa Solomon bagha izi.  
\v 25 Atrivir kaba azenibar vaghvagha Solomon bagha bizir aghuiba isa izava a gan…®di. Me bizir gumaziba silva ko gol…®n ingariziba ko, korotiar aghuiba ko, afuziba ko, pauran igharagha garir mughuriar aghuiba zuiba ko, hoziaba ko, donkiba, a bagha da isa izi. 
\p  
\v 26 \x - \xo 10:26 \xt 1 Atriviba 4:26\x*Solomon dughiabar zurara m…®dorozir karisba ko, uan m…®dorozir gumaziba bagha hoziaba isi. Egha a karisba ko hoziaba da ikiasa a inabazir nguibar ekiabar ada ar…®ki, ez…® maba a ko Jerusalem…®n iti. A 1,400plan karisba ikia, egha 12,000pla hoziaba iti.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 10:27 \xt God…®n Araziba 17:17\x*Solomon atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, a temer sidan av…®riba ko silvan av…®riba inigha Jerusalem…®n ize. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n silvan av…®riba ikia, dag…®ar k…®nibar m…®n pura tintinibar irav iti. Egha uaghan temer sidan bar av…®riba iti, mati temer Israel…®n m…®ghs…®ar muziaribar izezibar m…®n iti.  
\v 28 \x - \xo 10:28 \xt God…®n Araziba 17:16\x*Solomon uan hoziaba, kantri Musri\f + \fr 10:28 \ft Kantri Musri, kantri Lebanon…®n not…®n amadaghan iti. Ez…® gumazir maba ghaze, a kantri Isip…®n m…®gei.\f* ko kantri Silisian da ini. A dag…®ar ingangaribagh amir gumaziba amadima, me Silisian ghua a bagha hoziabagh ivesi.  
\v 29 Ez…® dag…®aba bagha ingangaribagh amir gumazir kaba, Musrin karisba ko hoziabagh ivesi. Karisba vaghvagha dar ivezim 6,000 kinan tu, ez…® hoziaba vaghvagha dar ivezim 1,500 kinan tu. Egha dag…®ar ingangaribagh amir gumazir kaba, me karisba ko hoziaba isa ghua da amadima, Hitia ko Siriabar atriviba dagh ivesi. 
\c 11  
\s1 Solomon ak…®rim ragha God gasara 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 11:1 \xt God…®n Araziba 17:17\x*Solomon kantrin igharazibar amizir av…®rim gifonge. A faragha Isipian atrivim…®n guivim…®n ikia, egha uaghan kantri Moap…®n amizibar ikia, egha kantri Amon…®n amiziba ko, kantri Idom…®n amiziba, ko Saidon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amiziba, ko Hitian amizibar iti.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 11:2 \xt Ua Me Ini 34:16; God…®n Araziba 7:3-4\x*Nguibar kabar amiziba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God faragha, men ikian Israelian anogoroke. Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa Israel…®n azenan itir amizir kabar ikian bar mark…®. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, guizbang…®ra, me ia gekut…® ia na ategh men asebar g…®n mangam.‚Äù Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®fa. Ez…® puvat…®, Solomon amizir kabagh ifongeghav…®ra iti.  
\v 3 Solomon amuir 700pla ikia, amuir dozir 300pla iti. Ez…® amizir kaba an n…®ghn…®zim g…®raz…®, an ak…®rim ragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God gasara.  
\v 4 Solomon ghurizir dughiam…®n, amizir kaba an navir averiam g…®raz…® a men asebar g…®n zui. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Solomon uan afeziam Devit…®n araziba ategha, egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, an God…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.  
\v 5 Solomon aser kam Astarten ziam fe, kar Saidonian aser amizim. Egha a uaghan asem Molek…®n ziam fe, a Amonian asem, ez…® an amizir arazim bar ikuviz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar an aghua.  
\v 6 Solomon kamagh…®n amua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kuram gami. A uan afeziam Devit…®n arazir aghuiba ategha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n arazim guiz…®n an g…®n zuir puvat…®.  
\v 7 A uaghan, aser kam Kemos…®n ziam fasa danganir mam…®n ingari, kar Moapian aser arazir bar kurir God bar aghuazibagh amim. A uaghan Molek…®n ziam fasa danganir mam…®n ingari, kar Amonian aser arazir bar kurir God bar aghuazibagh amim. Danganir kamning, aning Jerusalem…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n m…®ghs…®am gis…®n iti.  
\v 8 Egha a uaghan uan amuir azenan itir kaba bagha danganir mabar ingari, eght…® me dar mang…®va ofan m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuim ko, ofan igharagha gariba uan aseba bagh dar amuam. 
\p  
\v 9-10 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, a faragha dughiar pumuning…®n Solomon batogha aser kabar ziaba fan an anogoroke. Ez…® Solomon Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar Gavgavim batuegha, ak…®rim ragha a gasara. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God adarim Solomon…®n ikia,  
\v 11 egha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh! N…® uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua, arazir k…® ifongeziba ko nan Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim abigha, nan Akar Gavgavim…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® kamagh…®n n…®ghnigha g…®vagha ghaze, n…® atrivir ingangarim…®n g…®vagh, ua kantrin kam…®n ganan kogham. K…® n…®n ingangarir gumazitam am…®seveght…®ma an atrivim…®n otivam.  
\v 12 N…® aremeght…® n…®n otarim atrivim…®n ik…®t…®ma, k…® a batuegham. K…® n…®n afeziam Devit g…®n…®ghn…®gha, dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® batueghan kogham.  
\v 13 Egh k…® atrivir ingangarim…®n bar a batueghan kogham. Puvat…®. K…® uan ingangarir gumazim Devit ko, nguibar ekiar k…® ua baghav…®ra inabazim, k…® aning g…®n…®ghn…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® n…®n otarim ateght…® a Israelian anaba tam…®n atrivim…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
\s1 Gumazir pumuning Solomon…®n apanim gami 
\p  
\v 14 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gumazir mam gamiz…®ma, a Solomon…®n apanim…®n oto. Gumazir kam…®n ziam Hadat, a Idomian atrivim…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazir mam.  
\v 15 Atrivim Devit fom…®ra Idomia ko m…®soke. Ez…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim Joap, a Idom…®n ghugha, m…®dorozim…®n ariaghirezir gumazibar kuaba afe.  
\v 16 Joap uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko me iak…®nir 6plan Idom…®n kantrin ikia gumazibav sogha ghua bar me kuavareme.  
\v 17 Dughiar kam…®n Hadat suvighav…®ra ikia, egha Idom…®n gumazir maba ko ara Isip…®n kantrin zui. Gumazir kaba, kar an afeziam…®n ingangarir gumaziba.  
\v 18 Me Midian…®n nguazim ategha ghua Paran…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n otifi. Egha Paran…®n gumaziba inigha, me bar mogh…®ra Isip…®n ghue. Me otivigha g…®vagha, ghua Isip…®n atrivim batoz…®ma a nguazir as…®zir mam ko, d…®penir mam Hadat ganigha, daghebar an akurvasi.  
\v 19 Isipian atrivim bar Hadat gifongegha anetaghiz…®ma, a Tapenes…®n afumim…®n iti. Tapenes, a Isip…®n atrivim…®n amuim.  
\v 20 Ez…® Hadat…®n amuim otarir mam bate, ez…® me ziam Genubat a gat…®. Ez…® Tapenes Genubat inigha Isipian atrivim…®n boriba sara atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n men gari.  
\v 21 Ez…® Hadat Isip…®n ikia orazi, Devit ko an m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim Joap, aning areme. A kamagh…®n oregha ghua Isipian atrivim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® nan amamangat…®ght…®, k…® uamategh uan kantrin mangam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® atrivim an azara, ‚ÄúN…® manmaghsua uamategh uan kantrin mangasa? N…® na ko ikia bizitabar otevez ti.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® Hadat a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® bizitam gasazir puvat…®. K…® kamaghsua, n…® pura na ateght…® k…® mangam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23 God gumazir igharazir mam uaghan a gamiz…®ma, a Solomon…®n apanim…®n oto. Gumazir kam…®n ziam Reson, a Eliadan otarim. Reson a kantri Soban Atrivim Hadateser…®n ingangarir gumazir mam. An Hadateser ategha arav ghu.  
\v 24 Egha a gumazir maba akuvagha men faragha ghua, tintinibar puram arua, gumazamizibav sogha men biziba okei. Ez…® Devit fom…®ra Hadateser…®n m…®dorozir gumazibav sogha me ag…®vaz…®,\f + \fr 11:24 \ft N…® 2 Samuel 8:3-6 ko 10:15-19…®n gan.\f* bizir kam…®n g…®n, Reson uan adarazi ko me ghua Damaskus…®n nguibar ekiam…®n iti. Egha an adarazi an akuraz…®, a Damaskus…®n atrivim…®n oto.  
\v 25 Ez…® Solomon atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Reson zurara Israelian apanim gami, Hadat amiz…® mok…®n. Egha Reson kantri Sirian atrivim…®n ikia, Israelia bar men aghua. 
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Jeroboam bagha akam ak…®ri 
\p  
\v 26 Solomon…®n ingangarir gumazir dapanir mam uaghan ak…®rim ragha a gasaragha an apanim gami. An ziam Jeroboam. An afeziam…®n ziam Nebat, ez…® an amebam…®n ziam Serua. Ez…® an afeziam Nebat areme. Jeroboam, a Seredan nguibam…®n gumazim. Kar Efraim…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n itir nguibar ekiam.  
\v 27 Jeroboam Atrivim Solomon ab…®nasa n…®ghn…®si. Bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamagh…®n ghu, Solomon Jerusalem…®n danganir iraghueziba apeava, Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazim ak…®rir dughiam…®n,  
\v 28 Jeroboam bar deraghav…®ra ingari. Solomon an ingangarir aghuir kabar ganigha anem…®sevez…® a Josep…®n anabam…®n adarazir gativagha men gari. Ingangarir kaba, atrivim da isa me gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 29 Dughiar mam…®n, Jeroboam Jerusalem ategha tuavir mam…®n zuima, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Ahiya, a Silon gumazim, a iza tuavim…®n a bato. Aning uaningra itima, gumazitam uam aning ko itir puvat…®. Dughiar kam…®n, Ahiya korotiar igiar mam arugha egha ize.  
\v 30 Egha Ahiya korotiar igiar kam suegha, an suiragha 12plan akuabar aneb…®ki.  
\v 31 Egha a Jeroboam…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, kamagh…®n n…® m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® gan! K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® atrivir ingangarim…®n Solomon ag…®vasa n…®ghnigha g…®fa. K…® n…® damight…® n…® Israelian anabar 10pla gativagh men ganam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® korotiar akuar 10pla ua bagh dar suikigh.  
\v 32 K…® uan ingangarir gumazim Devit ko, Israel…®n anababar tong…®n Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiar k…® ua baghav…®ra inabazim, k…® aning g…®n…®ghn…®si. Kamagh…®n, k…® Solomon ateght…®, an anabar vam…®ran ganam.  
\v 33 Israelia ak…®rim ragha na gasaragha Saidon…®n aser amizim Astarten ko, Moapian asem Kemos, ko, Amonian asem Molek, me men ziaba fe. Me tuavir aghuir k…® men akaziba dar g…®n zuir puvat…®gha, nan arazir k…® ifongeziba ko, bizir k…® damuasa ia m…®kemezibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Egha k…® ifongezir puvat…®zir biziba me dagh ami. Me Solomon…®n afeziam Devit…®n arazir aghuiba bar ada ataki. Ez…® bizir kam bang…®n k…® arazir kam men akagham. 
\p  
\v 34 ‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòEgh k…® atrivir ingangarim…®n Solomon da bar aneg…®vaghan kogham. K…® uan ingangarir gumazir k…® ua bagha m…®sevezim Devit, a g…®n…®ghn…®si. A nan Akar Gavgaviba ko arazir k…® ifongeziba bar dar g…®n zuir gumazim. K…® a g…®n…®ghn…®gh, Solomon aneteght…® an atrivim…®n ik…® mang…® aremegham.  
\v 35 Solomon aremegh g…®vaght…®, an otarim an danganim inigh atrivim…®n ik…®t…®, k…® an dafarim…®n 10plan Israelian anababa inigh n…® Jeroboam, n…®n dafarim dar…®gham.  
\v 36 Egh k…® Solomon…®n otarim ateght…®, a Israelian anabar vam…®ran ganam. Eght…® nan ingangarir gumazim Devit…®n lam mungueghan kogham.\f + \fr 11:36 \ft 2 Samuel 21:17…®n, gumazir maba ghaze, Devit mati lam, angazangarim Israelia gan…®di. G…®n akar kam, Devit…®n lam, a Devit…®n adarazir akar is…®n zuim…®n m…®n oto. Akar kam, ‚ÄúDevit…®n lam mungan kogham,‚Äù an m…®ngarim kamagh…®n, ‚ÄúDevit…®n ik…®zim g…®van mark…®.‚Äù\f* Bar puvat…®gham. An ovavir boriba atrivibar ik…® mang…®v…®ra ikiam. Devit…®n ik…®zim…®n adarazir tong…®n gumazitam zurara Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n ikiam. Nguibar ekiar kam, gumazamiziba an iz…®va nan borogh…®n iz…® nan ziam fasa k…® a ginaba.  
\v 37 Jeroboam, k…® n…® damight…®ma n…® Israelian atrivim…®n otogh, nguazir n…® ganasa ifongeziba, n…® bar dagh ativagh dar ganam.  
