\v 10 Ez…® ingangarir gumazir igiar kaba kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® men azangs…®zir n…®n afeziam me gamizir os…®mt…®zir kataba ikarvaghs…®, n…® kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòIa ghaze, nan afeziam paza ia gami, a? Puvat…®. Kar pura bizim. Nan dafarir tereghiam, bar nan afeziam…®n gavgavim gafira.  
\v 11 Guizbang…®ra nan afeziam os…®mt…®zim ia gan…®ngi, ez…® k…® os…®mt…®zir ekiar bar av…®riba ia dan…®ngam. Nan afeziam benim…®n ia ifozoroke, ez…® k…® benir gavgavir atariba itibar ia fozoroght…®, ian inivaf…®ziba asighiram.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
