\v 16 \x - \xo 12:16 \xt 2 Samuel 20:1\x*Gumazamiziba me dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, atrivim men akam bareghan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me pamtem…®n d…®a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE Devit…®n adarazir apengan ikian aghua. E Devit…®n adarazi puvat…®, e uaghan Devit…®n otarir kam…®n adarazi puvat…®. E Israel…®n gumazamiziba bar uamategh uan nguibabar mangam. Eght…® ia Devit…®n adarasi, ia uarira uarir gan.‚Äù Me akar kam m…®kemegha, me tintinibar uan nguibabar ghue.  
\v 17 Ez…® Israelian marazi uaghan Judan nguibar ekiabar ikia, Judabar tong…®n iti. Ez…® Atrivim Rehoboam men gari. 
