\v 18 Egha g…®n Atrivim Rehoboam Adoniram amadaz…®ma, a Israelia bagha zui. Adoniram, a fom…®ra gumazir atrivim…®n ingangaribagh amir gumazibar garir gumazim. An ziar igharazim Adoram. Dughiar Adoniram ghua Israelia batozim…®n, me bar mogh…®ra dag…®abar a giniviz…®ma an areme. Ez…® Rehoboam bizir kam…®n akam baregha, zuam…®ra uan karis…®n ghuavanabogha ara Jerusalem…®n ghu.  
\v 19 Dughiar kam…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n,\f + \fr 12:19 \ft Akar kam, ‚Äúdughiar kam…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n,‚Äù a dat…®r…®gh…®n en dughiar kam m…®geir puvat…®. A gumazir ak…®nafarir kam osirizim…®n dughiam m…®gei.\f* Israelian not…®n amadaghan itiba me akaba batoghav…®ra iti, me Devit…®n ik…®zim…®n tav atrivim…®n otogh men ganan me bar aghua. 
\p  
