\v 24 ‚ÄòK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: Ia mang…® Israelia m…®soghan mark…®, me ian adarasi. Guizbang…®ra, k…® uab…® kamagh…®n amiz…®, Israelia ian bighiaghir…®. Kamagh…®n ia uamategh uan nguibabar mang…®.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù Ez…® Semaia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam me m…®k…®niz…®, me uamategha uan nguibabar ghue. 
\s1 Jeroboam ak…®rim ragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God gasara 
