\p  
\v 20 Aning dagheba apir dakozim…®n aperaghav itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, akar mam isa akam inigha izir gumazir ghurir kam gan…®ngi.  
\v 21 Ez…® akam inigha izir gumazir ghurir kam, Judan akam inigha izir gumazir kam pamtem a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® an Akar Gavgavim batuegha, egha a n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n amizir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.  
\v 22 N…® ua iza danganir a dagheba ko d…®pabar aman n…®n anogoroghez…®, n…® da ame. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® aremeght…® me n…®n kuam is…® n…®n inazir afeziabar mozim…®n n…® afaghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 23 Ez…® Judan akam inigha izir gumazim amegha g…®vaz…®, akam inigha izir gumazir ghurim, a bagha uan donki ak…®righa a gan…®ngiz…® ana gaperagha zui.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 13:24 \xt 1 Atriviba 20:36\x*A ghuav…®ra itima laion…®n mam iza a batogha a m…®soghez…® an areme. Ez…® an kuam ir…®ghav itima donki an borogh…®n tughav itima, laion uaghan an kuam…®n borogh…®n tughav iti.  
\v 25 Ez…® g…®n gumazir maba tuavir kam…®n ghua garima, an kuam tuavim…®n ir…®ghav itima, laion an borogh…®n tughav iti. Ez…® me ghua Betel…®n nguibam…®n otivigha ganizir bizir kam…®n gun gumazamizibav gei. 
\p  
\v 26 Ez…® akam inigha izir gumazir ghurim akar kam baregha ghaze, ‚ÄúMar Judabar akam inigha izir gumazim…®n kuamra. A Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam batoke. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, m…®kemez…® mogh…®ram amua laion amadaz…®, a iza a m…®soghez…® an areme.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 27 Ez…® a uan otaribav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa satel is…® nan donki gis…®n anet…®gh.‚Äù Ez…® a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n me ami.  
\v 28 Ez…® a tuavim…®n ghua garima akam inigha izir gumazim…®n kuam tuavim…®n ir…®ghav iti. Ez…® donki ko laion an kuam…®n borogh…®n tughav iti. Laion…®n kam, an kuam apir puvat…®gha, bizitam…®n donki gamizir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® akam inigha izir gumazir ghurir kam an kuam isa uan donki gat…®. Egha a inigha Betel…®n ghugha, an kuam bagha azia, a isa mozim…®n anefam.  
\v 30 Egha akam inigha izir gumazir ghurim an kuam isa uan dag…®ar torimram anefa. Egha uan otariba ko azia kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúO, en aveghbuam! O, en aveghbuam, noki!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 31 \x - \xo 13:31 \xt 2 Atriviba 23:17-18\x*Me anefagha g…®vagha, akam inigha izir gumazir ghurim kamagh…®n uan otaribav gei, ‚ÄúK…® aremeght…® ia nan kuam is…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kam…®n kuam itir mozim…®n borogh…®n na afagh.  
\v 32 Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, akar an akam inigha izir gumazim m…®kemezibar amight…®, da bar guizbang…®rama otivigham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Betel…®n itir ofa gamir dakozim gas…®ghsigh, egh Samarian Distrigh…®n itir nguibabar itir asebar ziaba feir d…®peniba bar dagh as…®ghasigham.‚Äù 
\s1 Jeroboam arazir kuram gamua ghuav…®ra iti 
\p  
\v 33 Jeroboam bizir kabar gari da otifi, ez…® a uan arazir kuraba atagh…®raghasa n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. An ofa damuamin danganir a uab…® ingarizibar ofa damuasa gumazir k…®nibav s…®va ghuav…®ra iti. Gumazir manam ofa damuamin ingangarim bagha n…®ghn…®si, Jeroboam puram anem…®seveght…®, a ingaram.  
\v 34 Jeroboam uan adarazi ko me arazir kurar kabagh amua, men arazir kurar kaba me gamima me os…®mt…®zim iti. Arazir kam bang…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Jeroboam…®n adarazi bar me kuavareme. 
\c 14  
\s1 Jeroboam…®n otarim ar…®mariam ini 
\p  
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n, Atrivim Jeroboam…®n otarim Abiya ar…®mariam a ini.  
\v 2 Ez…® Jeroboam kamagh…®n uan amuim…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® kamagh…®n ifonge, n…® igharagh kurkeght…®, gumazamiziba suam, n…® nan amuim puvat…®. Egh n…® Silon mang…®. N…® fo, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Ahiya a nguibar kam…®n iti. Gumazir kam na m…®g…®a ghaze, k…® Israelian atrivim…®n otivam.  
\v 3 N…® 10plan bret…®n rubuziba ko, bisket…®n taba ko, hanin m…®netam inigh mang…® a dan…®ngigh. Egh otarim…®n ar…®mariam g…®fofoghs…® an azaragh. Eght…® a n…® m…®k…®mam.‚Äù  
\v 4 Ez…® Jeroboam…®n amuim a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ghua Silon nguibam…®n Ahiyan d…®penim…®n zui. Ahiya dat…®r…®gh…®n bar ghurigha damaziba okafi. 
\p  
\v 5 Jeroboam…®n amuim izav…®ra itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Ahiyan m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúJeroboam…®n amuim n…® bagh iz…®, uan otarim…®n ar…®mariam g…®fofoghs…® n…®n azangs…®ghasa izi, a deragham ti. A ifar amizir igharazim…®n m…®n gan n…® bagh izam.‚Äù Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, biziba bar dar gun Jeroboam…®n amuim m…®k…®masa Ahiya m…®keme. 
\p  
\v 6 Ez…® Ahiya orazima, Jeroboam…®n amuim…®n dagariba tiar akam…®n azenan t…®ngazima a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúJeroboam…®n amuim n…® aven iz…®. N…® tizim bagh amizir igharazim…®n m…®n uab…® gar…®gha na gifarasa? K…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar mam iti, k…® n…® m…®kemeght…® n…®n navim bar n…® basemegham.  
\v 7 N…® uamategh Jeroboam bagh mang…®, kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam…®n a m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: Jeroboam, k…® uan gumazamiziba Israelia, men tong…®n n…® am…®sevez…® n…® men atrivim…®n oto.  
\v 8 K…® Devit…®n adarazi da atrivir ingangarim adegha, a isa n…® gan…®ngi. Ez…® n…® nan ingangarir gumazim Devit amizir arazir aghuibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. Devit nan Akar Gavgaviba bar adar g…®n ghua, uan navir averiam…®n aven na baghav…®ra ikia, egha arazir nan damazim…®n derazibaram ami.  
\v 9 N…® arazir kuram gamua ghuav…®ra ikia, faragha ikezir darazir arazir kuraba bar dagh afira. N…® ua bagha god…®n igharaziba ko marvir guar n…® ain…®n amerezibar dar ingari. Egha ak…®rim ragha na gasaragha aser kabar ziaba fe. Ez…® k…® n…®n arazir kaba bagha, bar n…®n an…®ngaghe.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 14:10 \xt 1 Atriviba 15:29\x*Bar guizbang…®ra! K…® n…®n adarazigh as…®ghasigham. Egh Jeroboam, Israelian aven n…®n gumaziba g…®n otivt…®, k…® bar mogh…®ra me ag…®vagham, gumazir igiaba ko aruaba sara. K…® bar me ag…®vagham, mati gumazim buariba bar da suegha da makuniz…® tam ua itir puvat…®.  
\v 11 N…®n adarazir aven gumazitaba nguibar ekiam…®n ar…®m…®ghiregh men kuaba ik…®t…®, afiaba dar amam. Eght…® tarazi nguibar ekiam…®n azenan ar…®m…®ghireght…® isaba men kuabar amam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Egha Ahiya ua Jeroboam…®n amuim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® uamategh uan nguibam…®n mang…®. N…® nguibar ekiam…®n aven mang…®t…®m…®ra n…®n otarim aremegham.  
\v 13 Eght…® Israelia bar mogh…®ra an aziva anefam. A uab…®ra Jeroboam…®n adarazir tong…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, an garima, an arazir aghuibagh ami. An kuamra gumaziba a is…® mozim dar…®gham. Eght…® Jeroboam…®n adarazir gumazir igharaziba, puvat…®gham.  
\v 14 Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gumazitam am…®seveght…® an atrivim…®n ikiam, egh atrivir kam Jeroboam…®n adarazi bar me ag…®vagham. Bizir kam, dat…®r…®gh…®n ikegh mang…®v…®ra ikiam.\f + \fr 14:14 \ft Hibrun akam, deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\p  
\v 15 ‚ÄúIsraelia, temer guarir aser amizim Aseran nedazim itiba dar ziaba fe, men arazir kam Ikiav…®ra Itir God gamiz…®, a bar men an…®ngaghe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, m…®zazim me gaseght…®, me atiatigh akongam, mati aperiam uaghira ighurunim amozorozi a ivazvasi. Egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nguazir aghuir a Israelian inazir afeziabagh an…®ngizir kam…®n me batuegham. Egh Yufretis…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n tintinibar me aghamsigh me akunigham.  
\v 16 Jeroboam uab…® arazir kurar kam gamigha, bar Israelia gekuiz…® me arazir kuram gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelian arazir kurar kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh, ak…®rim ragh me gasaragham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® Jeroboam…®n amuim akar kaba baregha d…®kavigha uamategha Tirsan nguibar ekiam…®n zui. A ghua uan d…®penim…®n aven zuima, an otarim areme.  
\v 18 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Ahiya m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra, Israelia bar mogh…®ra otarim…®n azia, egha a isa mozim gat…®. 
\s1 Jeroboam areme 
\p  
\v 19 Atrivim Jeroboam amizir araziba, da bar ak…®nafarir mam…®n aven iti, ak…®nafarir kam me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.\f + \fr 14:19 \ft En God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n aven, ak…®nafarir pumuning iti, me kamagh…®n aning d…®bora ghaze, Israelia ko Judabar Atriviba 1 ko, Israelia ko Judabar Atriviba 2. Ez…® uaghan ak…®nafarir igharazir pumuning iti, me aning d…®bora ghaze, Atrivibar Eghaghaniba 1 ko, Atrivibar Eghaghaniba 2. Ez…® marazi kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, bar fom…®ra ak…®nafarir igharazimning uaghan ike, Kar, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba ko, Judan Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. Dughiar mabar, God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n aven itir ak…®nafariba, ak…®nafarir igharazir kamning…®n akaba dar iti. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ak…®nafarir igharazir kamning, bar ovenge, ez…® e uam adar ganan kogham.\f* Ak…®nafarir kam…®n, a uan apanibav soghezir eghaghaniba ko, a kantri gativagha amizir bizibar eghaghaniba, an aven iti.  
\v 20 Jeroboam 22plan azenibar atrivim…®n ikegha uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me an kuam isa anefa. Ez…® an otarim Nadap an danganim inigha atrivim…®n iti. 
\s1 Rehoboam Judabar atrivim…®n iti 
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 11:5--12:16) 
\p  
\v 21 Solomon…®n otarim Rehoboam, a Judabar atrivim…®n iti. A 41plan azeniba ikia, egha atrivim…®n oto, egha 17plan azenibar atrivim…®n ike. A Jerusalem…®n aperagha iti, nguibar ekiar kam Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian nguibar ekiar igharazibar tong…®n, ua bagha a ginaba, eght…® danganir kam…®n Israelia bar God…®n borogh…®n iz…®va an ziam fam. Rehoboam…®n amebam, an ziam Nama, a kantri Amonian amizim. 
\p  
\v 22 Dughiar kam…®n Judabar gumazamiziba arazir kurar av…®riba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami. Ez…® arazir kurar me amizir kaba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n an…®ngagharim gamiz…®, a ghua bar ekefe. Men inazir afeziaba faragha arazir kurabagh ami, ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n adarir dat…®r…®gh…®n Judabar itim, a bar ekevegha adarir fom…®ra men inazir afeziabar ikezim bar a gafira.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 14:23 \xt 2 Atriviba 17:9-10\x*Judaba dat…®r…®gh…®n m…®ghs…®aba ko temer ekiabar apebabar, dag…®ar guarir d…®ghoriba itiba ko temer guarir aser amizim Aseran nedazim itiba, isa danganir kabar da asava dar ziaba fe.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 14:24 \xt God…®n Araziba 23:17\x*Ez…® arazir bar kurar mam oto. Gumazir maba, me asebar ziaba fer danganir kabar poroghamiba uari isava akuir arazibagh ami. Judan gumazamiziba, me gumazamizir fom…®ra nguazir kam…®n ikezibar m…®n, arazir bar kurir k…® aghuazibagh ami. Gumazamizir fom…®ra ikezir kaba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God me batuegha, nguazir kam isa Israelia gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 25 \x - \xo 14:25 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 12:2-8\x*Ez…® Rehoboam atrivim…®n itima an namba 5…®n azenim otoz…®, Isipian Atrivim Sisak uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko iza Jerusalem ko m…®sosi.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 14:26 \xt 1 Atriviba 10:16-17; 2 Eghaghaniba 9:15-16\x*Egha me Jerusalemia m…®sogha, me ab…®nigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ko, atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n bizir bar aghuiba, me bar da ini. Egha uaghan Solomon m…®dorozim bagha ingarigha gol…®n noghezir oraba, me bar ada inigha Isip…®n ghue.  
\v 27 Ez…® g…®n Atrivim Rehoboam uan ingangarir gumazibav kemez…®, me bras inigha uam orar igiabar ingarigha bras…®n da noke. Ez…® da Isipia okemezir orabar danganiba ini. Ez…® Rehoboam da isa, ingangarir gumazir an d…®penim…®n tiar akabagh eghuvibagh an…®ngiz…® me dar suigha tiarakabar gari.  
\v 28 Atrivim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n zuir dughiabar, a geghuvir gumazir kaba orar kaba inigh an aku mangam. Eght…® atrivim uamategh uan d…®penim…®n izeght…®, me orar kaba inigh da itir d…®penim…®n mang…® dar arigham. 
\p  
\v 29 Atrivim Rehoboam amizir arazir igharaziba, da ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n aven iti, Judabar Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.  
\v 30 Rehoboam ko Jeroboam aning atrivimning…®n itir dughiam…®n, kantrin pumuning zurara uaning m…®sosi.  
\v 31 Ez…® g…®n Rehoboam uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®ma, me Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n an inazir afeziabar kuaba afir danganim…®n anefa. Ez…® an otarim Abiya an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. Rehoboam…®n amebam an ziam Nama, a kantri Amon…®n amizim. 
\c 15  
\s1 Abiya Judan atrivim…®n oto 
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 13:1--14:1) 
\p  
\v 1 Nebat…®n otarim Jeroboam, Israel…®n atrivim…®n itima, an namba 18…®n azenim…®n, gumazir ziam Abiya, an ziar igharazim Abijam, a Judan atrivim…®n oto.  
\v 2 A 3plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti. Ez…® an amebam…®n ziam Maka, Apsalom…®n guivim.  
\v 3 Abiya arazir kurar an afeziam amizibar m…®raram ami. A uan inazim Devit amiz…® mogh…®n, a bar uab…® isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God, an God gan…®dir puvat…®gha, a ko navir vam…®ran itir puvat…®.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 15:4 \xt 1 Atriviba 11:36\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Devit bang…®n, an otarir mam isa Abiya gan…®ngi, an an danganim inigh Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n ikiam. Eght…® a Jerusalem damight…®, a deraghv…®ra ik…® gavgavigham.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 15:5 \xt 2 Samuel 11:1-27\x*Devit Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh ami, egha zurara an Akar Gavgavibar g…®n zui. Dughiar bar vam…®ra, Devit pazav Hitian gumazim Uria gami.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 15:6 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 13:3-21\x*Abiya angam…®ra itir dughiam…®n,\f + \fr 15:6 \ft Hibrun ak…®nafarir bar ghuriba, danganir kam…®n, dar akaba ko uaghara garir puvat…®. Dar av…®riba, ziar kam, Rehoboam dar iti, ez…® vabara ziar kam, Abiya dar iti.\f* Rehoboam…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba, ko Jeroboam…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba, zurara uariv soghav…®ra iti.  
\v 7 Atrivim Abiya amizir arazir igharaziba, da ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n aven iti, Judabar Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. 
\p  
\v 8 Abiya uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n aven anefa, ez…® an otarim Asa an danganim inigha atrivim…®n iti. 
\s1 Asa Judabar atrivim…®n oto 
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 15:16--16:14) 
\p  
\v 9 Jeroboam Israelian atrivim…®n itima, an azenir namba 20…®n, Asa Judan atrivim…®n oto.  
\v 10 Asa 41plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti. An inaghamim Maka, an Apsalom…®n guivim.  
\v 11 Asa uan inazim Devit…®n m…®n arazir aghuir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n derazibagh ami.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 15:12 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 15:8-15\x*Egha Asa asebar ziaba fer danganibar, gumazir poroghamiba uari bak…®a uari koma akuir arazim gamiba, a bar me batoke. Egha an inazir afeziaba d…®ghoregha asezir asebar marvir guaba, a bar da batoke. 
\p  
\v 13 Egha uan inaghamim Maka, atrivir danganim…®n a batoke. Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar aghuazir aser amizim Asera, Maka an nedazim…®n ingari, ez…® atrivim an danganim…®n a batoke. Egha nedazir kurar kam okegha a inigha ghua Kidron…®n Fanem…®n danganir zarim…®n a gaboroz…® a isi. 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® asebar ziaba fer danganir bar p…®n itiba ikiav…®ra iti. Asa dagh as…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. Egha dughiabar zurara Asan navir averiam Ikiav…®ra Itir God baghav…®ra iti.  
\v 15 Egha Asa, an afeziam Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha inabazir biziba ko a uab…® inabaziba, kar silvaba ko gol ko itarir igharagha gariba, a da inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ghu. 
\p  
\v 16 Egha Asa ko Basa atrivimning…®n ikia, zurara uaning m…®sogha mamagh…®ra iti.  
\v 17 Basa dughiar mam…®n uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha ghua Judaba ko m…®sosi. Me Raman nguibar ekiam inigha, uam an d…®vazim…®n ingarigha anev…®ni, eght…® gumazamiziba Judan mang…®gh izegh damuan kogham.  
\v 18 Ez…® Atrivim Asa silva ko gol…®n nar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n itiba ko atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n itiba sara ini. Egha uan ingangarir gumazibagh an…®ngi, eght…® me da inigh nguibar ekiam Damaskus…®n mang…® Sirian Atrivim Benhadat dan…®ngam. Benhadat, a Taprimon…®n otarim, egha Hesion…®n igiavotarim. Asa kamagh…®n Benhadat m…®k…®masa uan ingangarir gumazibav keme,  
\v 19 ‚ÄúDat…®r…®gh…®n ga uaning ko akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim damigh, egh namakar aghuimning…®n ikiam, mati nan afeziam ko n…®n afeziam amiz…® mok…®n. K…® n…® bagha silva ko gol amadi. Eght…® n…® mang…® Israelian Atrivim Basa ko amizir akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavir mam ab…®kigh, eght…® a uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigh mang…® nan nguazim atakigh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® Atrivim Benhadat, Atrivim Asan m…®g…®r…®g…®am…®n amamangat…®gha, uan m…®dorozir gumazibar dapaniba amangiz…®, me ghua m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha ghua, Israelian nguibar ekiaba konasa ghue. Me ghua nguibar ekiar kaba kora, Ijon…®n nguibar ekiam isava, Dan ko Abel Betmaka ini. Egha uaghan Galilin D…®par Akarem…®n borogh…®n itir nguazim isava, Naptalin anabam…®n nguazim bar mogh…®ram a ini.  
\v 21 Ez…® Atrivim Basa kamagh…®n akam baraki, Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba iza Israelia m…®sosi, ez…® a ingangarir Raman nguibar ekiam…®n amim ategha, ua ghua Tirsan nguibar ekiam…®n iti. 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® g…®n Atrivim Asa Raman nguibam…®n mangasa, Judan gumaziba bar mogh…®ra me bagha akam amada. Ez…® me ghua, dag…®aba ko temer kaba bar da ini, kar Atrivim Basa gavgavim d…®vazim dan…®ngasa akuvazir biziba. Egha me da inigha zui, ez…® Asa da isa, Mispan nguibam av…®nizir d…®vazim ko Geban nguibar ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazim gavgavim aning gan…®ngi. Nguibar kamning, Benjamin…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n iti. 
\p  
\v 23 Atrivim Asa amizir arazir igharaziba, ko an gavgavir ekiaba, da ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n aven iti, Judabar Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. Ak…®nafarir kam, an Atrivim Asa nguibar ekiaba av…®nizir d…®vaziba, gavgavim dagh an…®ngizir ingangarir ekiaba ko ingangarir igharazir an amizibagh eghari. Ez…® Asa ghurigha g…®vaz…®, ar…®mariar kurar mam an dagarimning…®n oto.  
\v 24 Egha Asa uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…® me an kuam inigha Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n, an inazir afeziaba koma anefa. Ez…® an otarim Jehosafat, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. 
\s1 Nadap Israelian atrivim…®n iti 
\p  
\v 25 Asa namba 2…®n azenim…®n Judabar atrivim…®n itima, Jeroboam…®n otarim Nadap, Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha an azenir pumuningra atrivim…®n ike.  
\v 26 Egha Nadap uan afeziam…®n arazir kurabar g…®n ghua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n uab…® arazir kurabagh ami. Egha a uaghan Israelia getuima me uaghan arazir kurabagh ami. 
\p  
\v 27 Ez…® Isakar…®n anabam…®n gumazim Ahiya, an otarim Basa, a Nadap…®n m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa tuaviba buri. Ez…® Nadap uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghua Filistiaba ko m…®sogha, Gibeton…®n nguibar ekiam ek…®aruzir dughiam…®n, Basa, Nadap batogha a m…®soghez…® an areme.  
\v 28 Ez…® Asa uab…® Israelian atrivim…®n iti. Asa Judan atrivim…®n itima, an namba 3…®n azenim…®n, bizir kam oto.  
\v 29 \x - \xo 15:29 \xt 1 Atriviba 14:10; 14:14\x*Ez…® Basa zuam…®ra Jeroboam…®n adarazi bar me m…®suaghar…®ki. A men tav ataghiz…® a itir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. Ez…® arazir kam…®n, akar Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan ingangarir gumazim…®n akam…®n aven m…®kemezim, a guiz…®n oto. Akam inigha izir gumazim Ahiya, a Silon nguibam…®n gumazim.  
\v 30 Jeroboam…®n adarazir batozir bizim…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, Jeroboam faragha uab…® arazir kuram Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God…®n damazim…®n a gami, egha a uaghan Israelia getuima, me arazir kuram gami. Jeroboam…®n arazir kurar kaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God gamima, a bar an…®ngaghe, kamagh…®n amiz…® a Jeroboam…®n adarazigh as…®ghas…®ki. 
\p  
\v 31 Atrivim Nadap…®n arazir igharaziba, da ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n aven iti, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. 
\s1 Basa Israelian atrivim…®n oto 
\p  
\v 32-33 Asa namba 3…®n azenim…®n Judan atrivim…®n itima, Ahiyan otarim Basa, Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha a 24plan azenibar Tirsan nguibar ekiam…®n atrivim…®n ike. Dughiar Asa ko, Basa atrivimning…®n itim, aning uaning m…®soghav…®ra iti.  
\v 34 Egha Basa uan afeziam Jeroboam…®n m…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami. Egha a uaghan Israelia gekuiz…®, me arazir kurabagh ami. 
\c 16  
\p  
\v 1 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, akam Basa dan…®ngasa, akam inigha izir gumazim Jehu m…®keme, a Hananin otarim. Ikiav…®ra Itir God ghaze,  
\v 2 ‚ÄúBasa, n…® deraghv…®ram oragh. N…® faragha gumazir k…®nim, ez…® k…® n…® gamiz…® n…® atrivim…®n otogha, nan gumazamiziba Israelia gativagha men gari. Egha n…® Jeroboam…®n m…®n arazir kurabagh amua, gumazamizibagh etuima, me arazir kurabagh ami. Ez…® men arazir kuraba na gamima, k…® men an…®ngaghe.  
\v 3 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Nebat…®n otarim Jeroboam…®n adarazi gas…®ghas…®ghiz…® mogh…®n, k…® n…® ko n…®n adarasi, bar ia gas…®ghasigham.  
\v 4 N…®n adarazir aven gumazitaba, nguibar ekiam…®n ar…®m…®ghiregh men kuaba ik…®t…®, afiaba dar amam. Eght…® tarazi nguibar ekiam…®n azenan ar…®m…®ghireght…®, isaba men kuabar amam. K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 5 Atrivim Basa amizir arazir igharaziba, ko an gavgavir ekiaba bar, da ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n aven iti, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba.  
\v 6 Ez…® Basa uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me Tirsan anefa. Ez…® an otarim Ela an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. 
\p  
\v 7 Atrivim Basa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami, mati Atrivim Jeroboam fom…®ram amiz…® mogh…®n, ez…® an arazir kurar kaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God gamima an an…®ngaghe. Basa uaghan Jeroboam…®n adarazi bar me m…®suaghar…®ki. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Basa ko an adarazigh as…®ghas…®ghasa akam isa akam inigha izir gumazim Jehu gan…®ngi. Jeroboam…®n adarazi kuavaremez…® mogh…®n Basan adarazi uaghan kuavaremegham. 
\s1 Ela Israelian atrivim…®n oto 
\p  
\v 8 Atrivim Asa namba 26…®n azenim…®n, Judan atrivim…®n itima, Basan otarim Ela, Israel…®n atrivim…®n oto. Egha a Tirsan nguibar ekiam…®n azenir pumuningra atrivim…®n ike.  
\v 9 Ez…® Elan ingangarir gumazir mam, Simri, a Elan karis…®n mabar garir gumazibar dapanim, a Ela m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa tuaviba buri. Dughiar mam, Ela a Tirsan nguibar ekiam…®n ikia, Arsan d…®penim…®n d…®par onganiba apava ongani. Arsa, an atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n garir gumazim.  
\v 10 Ez…® Simri d…®penim…®n aven ghugha, Ela m…®soghez…® an areme, ez…® an an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. Asa Judan atrivim…®n itima, an namba 27…®n azenim…®n arazir kam oto. 
\p  
\v 11 Simri atrivim…®n otoz…® dughiam…®n, a zuam…®ra Basan adarazir gumaziba, bar me m…®suaghar…®ki. Egha uaghan an anababa ko namakaba bar me m…®suaghar…®ki. A tav ataghiz…® a itir puvat…®.  
\v 12 Kamagh…®n amiz…® Simri, Basan adarazi bar me ag…®fa. Arazir kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan akam isa akam inigha izir gumazim Jehu gan…®ngizim, a guiz…®n oto.  
\v 13 Basa uan otarim Ela ko, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, an damazim…®n arazir kuram gamua asebar ziaba fe. Egha Israelia gekuiz…®, me uaghan arazir kurabagh ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God an…®ngaghegha, bar Basan adarazigh as…®ghas…®ki.  
\v 14 Atrivim Ela amizir arazir igharaziba bar, da ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n aven iti, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. 
\s1 Simri Israelian atrivim…®n oto 
\p  
\v 15 Atrivim Asa namba 27…®n azenim…®n, Judan atrivim…®n itima, Simri Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha a Tirsan nguibar ekiam 7plan aruebar atrivim…®n ike. Dughiar kam…®n Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba kantri Filistian, Gibeton…®n nguibar ekiam iniasa anek…®arugha me ko m…®sosi.  
\v 16 Me m…®sogha ghua kamagh…®n oraki, Simri arazir bar kuram gamigha atrivim m…®soghez…® an areme. Ez…® aruer kamra, m…®dorozir gumaziba uan gumazir dapanim, an ziam Omri, me anem…®sevez…® a Israelian atrivim…®n oto.  
\v 17 Ez…® Omri uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko Gibeton ategha ghua, Tirsa iniasa an ek…®arugha m…®sosi.  
\v 18 Ez…® Simri Tirsan nguibar ekiam…®n garima, Omrin m…®dorozir gumaziba an adarazi ab…®ragha, nguibar ekiam isi, ez…® a ghua atrivim iti nagh…®n, d…®penir gavgavir mam…®n aven ghu. Egha an avim gaborogha atrivim…®n d…®penibagh aboi. Egha a uab…® avir kam…®n aven areme.  
\v 19 Bizir Simri batozim…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n: Jeroboam faragha uab…® arazir kuram Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God…®n damazim…®n a gami, egha a uaghan Israelia getuima, me arazir kuram gami. Ez…® Simri, Jeroboam…®n arazibar g…®n ghua, arazir kuram gamigha, an ivezir kurar kam ini.  
\v 20 Atrivim Simri amizir arazir igharaziba bar, da ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n aven iti, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. Ak…®nafarir kam, a Atrivim Ela ab…®razir eghaghanim, uaghan an aven iti. 
\s1 Omri Israelian atrivim…®n oto 
\p  
\v 21 Atrivim Simri aremez…®, Israelian ik…®zim bigha, ik…®zir pumuning…®n oto. Israelian gumazamizir maba, Ginat…®n otarim Tipni am…®seveght…®, an atrivim…®n ikiasava ami, ez…® igharaziba Omri baka.  
\v 22 Egha g…®n Omrin adarazi Tipnin adarazi ab…®ra. Ez…® Tipni aremez…®, Omri atrivim…®n oto. 
\p  
\v 23 Atrivim Asa namba 31…®n azenim…®n, Judan atrivim…®n itima, Omri Israelian atrivim…®n otogha 12plan azenibar atrivim…®n ike. An 6plan azenir faragha zuibar, a Tirsan nguibar ekiam…®n ike.  
\v 24 Egha g…®n Omri m…®ghs…®ar muziarim itir nguazir mam givese. Egha m…®ghs…®ar kam…®n d…®vazir gavgavim av…®nizir nguibar ekiar mam…®n ingari. Gumazir an a da nguazir kam givezezim, an ziam Semer, Omri 60,000 silva isa Semer gan…®ngi. Egha Omri gumazim Semer g…®n…®ghn…®gha ziar kam nguibar ekiam gan…®ngi, Samaria. 
\p  
\v 25 \x - \xo 16:25 \xt 1 Atriviba 14:9; 16:30-33; Maika 6:16\x*Egha Omri arazir kurar av…®rim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami. An arazir kuraba bar ekevegha atrivir, faragha ikezibar arazir kurabagh afira.  
\v 26 Omri, a Nebat…®n otarim Jeroboam…®n arazir kurabar g…®n ghua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n uab…® arazir kurabagh amua, uaghan Israelia getuima me arazir kurabagh ami, ez…® me aseba fer arazim, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israel…®n God gamiz…®, a puv…®ra men atari.  
\v 27 Atrivim Omri amizir arazir igharaziba bar, da ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n aven iti, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. Ak…®nafarir kam, a Omrin ingangarir gavgavibagh eghari.  
\v 28 Ez…® Omri uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n mozim…®n an efa. Ez…® an otarim Ahap, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. 
\s1 Ahap Israelian atrivim…®n oto 
\p  
\v 29 Atrivim Asa namba 38…®n azenim…®n, Judan atrivim…®n itima, Omrin otarim Ahap Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha a 22plan azenibar Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n ike.  
\v 30 Egha Ahap arazir kurar av…®rim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami. An arazir kuraba bar ekevegha atrivir faragha ikezibar arazir kurabagh afira.  
\v 31 A Jeroboam…®n m…®n arazir kurabagh amua, egha ghaze, pura bizim. Egha a Saidonian nguibam…®n Atrivim Etbal…®n guivim Jesebel…®n iti. Egha Saidonian asem Bal…®n ziam fe.  
\v 32 Egha Ahap asem Bal bagha Samarian d…®penir mam…®n ingarigha, ofa gamir dakozir mam d…®penir kam…®n aven an ingari.  
\v 33 Egha a dat…®r…®gh…®n aser amizim Aseran marvir guam…®n ingarigha, an ziam fe. An arazir kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, gamiz…®, a bar an an…®ngaghe. An arazir kuraba bar ekevegha, atrivir faragha ikezibar arazir kurabagh afira. 
\p  
\v 34 Dughiar Ahap atrivim…®n itim…®n, Betel…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazim Hiel, a ua Jerikon nguibar ekiam…®n ingari. Hiel nguibar ekiam…®n av…®namin d…®vazir m…®ngarim bagha dag…®ar ekiaba ar…®zima, an otarir ivariam Abiram areme. Egha a nguibam av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n tiar akar ekiabar ingarima, an otarir abuananam Segup areme. Bizir kam Hiel bato, mati akar Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar fom…®ra Nun…®n otarim Josua m…®kemezim…®n m…®n oto.\f + \fr 16:34 \ft N…® Josua 6:26…®n gan.\f* 
\c 17  
\ms1 Akam inigha izir gumazim Elaijan eghaghanim 
\mr (Sapta 17--21) 
\s1 Elaija ghaze, Israel…®n kantri, amoziba puvat…®gham 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 17:1 \xt Luk 4:25; Jems 5:17\x*Akam inigha izir gumazir mam, Elaija, a Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n itir nguibar ekiam Tisben gumazim. Dughiar mam…®n, a iza Atrivim Ahap batogha kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® God…®n ingangarir gumazim. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God…®n bar zurara itim, k…® an ziam…®n, guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei: Amoziba ko d…®magarim…®n ghuariam…®n d…®paba azenir tabar nguazim giran kogham. Egh kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…®t…® azenir taba g…®vagham. Egh kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…®t…®, k…® m…®kemeght…®, amozim ua izam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 2 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Elaija m…®gei,  
\v 3 ‚ÄúN…® danganir kam ategh, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n mang…®, Kerit…®n Daghurim…®n borogh…®n uab…® modogh ik…®.  
\v 4 Egh n…® daghurir kam…®n d…®pabar am…®. K…® kuarazir kotkotbav kemegha g…®fa, eght…® me n…® bagh dagheba inigh izam.‚Äù  
\v 5 Ez…® Elaija Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam…®n g…®n ghua, Jordan…®n Fanem…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n Kerit…®n Daghurim…®n borogh…®n iti.  
\v 6 A d…®par kam apa itima, kuarazir kotkotba m…®zaraziba ko guarat…®zibar, a bagha bretba ko as…®ziba isa izi, ez…® a dapi.  
\v 7 Ez…® dughiar mabar kantri Israel…®n amoziba puvat…®, ez…® daghurir d…®par kam uaghan dake. 
\s1 Elaija, amizim uan otarim ko aning…®n akura 
\p  
\v 8 Kerit…®n Daghurim dakegha g…®vaz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Elaija m…®gei,  
\v 9 \x - \xo 17:9 \xt Luk 4:25-26\x*‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh Saidon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n itir nguibar mam Sarefat…®n mang…®, egh kagh daperagh ik…®. N…® oragh, nguibar kam…®n, amizir mam iti, an pam areme. K…®, dagheba n…® dan…®ng…®va egh n…®n gan n…®n akurvaghasa, k…® amizir kam am…®sevegha a m…®keme.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Elaija d…®kavigha Sarefat…®n nguibam…®n ghu. A ghua nguibar kam…®n d…®vazim…®n tiar akam…®n otogha garima, amizir pam aremezir mam dazibagh eghufi. Ez…® an amizim…®n diagha an azaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGa uaning, k…® d…®patam amasa. N…® na bagh d…®patam m…®nem…®n a tuigh a inigh iz…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® amizim Elaijan akam baregha d…®pam iniasa zuima, a uam an diagha ghaze, ‚ÄúNoki, n…® na bagh bret…®n otevitam sara inigh iz…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® amizim a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, n…®n God…®n ikia mamagh…®ra itim, a nan gari. An ziam…®n, k…® guizbang…®ra m…®gei, k…® bretba puvat…®. Plauan bar muziarimra, a nguazir m…®nem…®n iti, ez…® oliv…®n borer muziarim, uan m…®sevim…®n iti. K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n plauan muziarim tuasa daziba akumakui, egh da inigh uan d…®penim…®n mang…®gh a tuam. K…® uan otarim ko, ga aneramegh g…®vaght…®, dagheba ua puvat…®gham. Mar ga ovengs…®v…®ra m…®zuam ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® Elaija a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® mamagh…®n n…®ghnigh atiatingan mark…®. N…® uan d…®penim…®n mang…®, n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra damu. Egh, n…® faragh plauan muziarir tam ko borem inigh egh bret…®n muziarim tuagh a inigh iz…® na dan…®ngigh, egh n…® g…®n uan otarim ko gua uaning bagh damu.  
\v 14 Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, a kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze: N…®n plauan muziarim ko borer muziarim ik…®v…®ra ik…®t…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uam amozim amadaght…® a ua nguazim gizam.‚Äù  
\v 15 Ez…® a d…®penim…®n ghugha Elaija a m…®kemez…® mogh…®ram ami. Egha amizir odiarir kam uan adarazi ko Elaija, me dughiabar damamin dagheba zurara iz…®vagha mamagh…®ra iti.  
\v 16 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, akam Elaija gan…®ngiz…®, a m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, an plauan m…®nem ko borer m…®sevim…®n itim g…®vazir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 17 Dughiar maba g…®vaz…®, d…®penir kam…®n ghuamizim…®n otarim arei. An ar…®mariam ghua bar ekevez…®ma an areme.  
\v 18 Ez…® amizim Elaija m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® God…®n ingangarir gumazim, n…® manmaghsua arazir kam…®n na gami? N…® ti kagh izegha nan arazir kuraba isa God…®n damazim gat…®, ez…® bizir kam bang…®n nan otarim areme.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® Elaija a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® otarim inigh iz…® na dan…®ngigh.‚Äù Egha Elaija otarim…®n kuam amebam…®n dafarimning…®n a inigha, a firagha d…®penim…®n p…®n itir ghuriam…®n ghuavanabogha uan dakozim…®n anet…®. 
\p  
\v 20 Egha a pamten Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n diagha ghaze, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® nan God. Amizir odiarir kam uan d…®penim nan taghiz…®, k…® a ko iti. Ez…® n…® manmaghsua os…®mt…®zir ekiar kam amizir kam gat…®gha, an otarim gamiz…®, an areme?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 21 \x - \xo 17:21 \xt 2 Atriviba 4:34-35\x*Egha Elaija dughiar 3plan uab…® am…®negha otarim gis…®n ir…®ghav ikia, kamagh…®n God…®n dia a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® nan God, n…® otarir kam damight…®, a ua d…®kavigh angam…®ra ik…®.‚Äù  
\v 22 \x - \xo 17:22 \xt Hibru 11:35\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Elaijan d…®mdiam baregha otarim gamiz…® a ua d…®kavigha angam…®ra iti. 
\p  
\v 23 Ez…® Elaija akui nagh…®n p…®n, otarim fegha a firagha izaghira an amebam gan…®ga, kamagh…®n an amebam m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® gan. N…®n otarim ua d…®kavigha angam…®ra iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 24 \x - \xo 17:24 \xt Jon 3:2; 16:30\x*Ez…® amebam a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, n…® God…®n ingangarir gumazim. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akar n…®n akatorim…®n otiviba, da bar guizbang…®ra.‚Äù 
\c 18  
\s1 Elaija ko asem Bal…®n akam inigha izir gumaziba 
\p  
\v 1 Aruem dughiar ruarim…®n iti, ez…® an dughiar namba 3…®n azenim…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Elaija m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® mang…® Atrivim Ahap…®n ganigh, eght…® k…® uam amozim amadaght…® a izam.‚Äù  
\v 2 Ez…® Elaija d…®kavigha Ahap bagha ghu. Dughiar kam…®n, Samariaba dagheba bar puvat…®. 
