\v 21 \x - \xo 18:21 \xt Josua 24:15; Matyu 6:24\x*Ez…® Elaija ghua gumazamizibar borogh…®n tughav ikia, kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir pumuning itiba, ia manad…®zogh…®n n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ra ikiam? Egh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a guizbang…®ra God, ia anar…®ra an ziam fam. Eght…® Bal a guizbang…®ra God, ia anar…®ra an ziam fam.‚Äù Ez…® gumazamiziba tong akatam ikarazir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®. 
