\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Benhadat ua me amangiz…®, me iza akar igharazim Ahap gan…®ga ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n uan m…®dorozir gumazir av…®riba inigh iz…®t…®, me n…®n nguibar ekiar kam gas…®ghasigham. Me bar bizibagh as…®ghasight…® da pura m…®nezibar m…®n iregham. K…® kamagh…®n damighan koght…®, nan aseba na m…®sueght…® k…® aremegham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Israelian atrivim a ikaragha kamagh…®n gumazir kabav g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa mang…® Benhadat kamagh…®n a m…®kemegh. Gumazim a guizbang…®ra m…®dorozir gumazim, a m…®soghs…® mangasa m…®dorozir sabam ikegha dia ifaghata uan ziam fer puvat…®. A m…®dorozim ag…®vagh egh g…®n uan ziam f…® bar akuegham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Dughiar kam…®n, Atrivim Benhadat atrivir igharazir maba ko, uan averpenibar ikia d…®par onganiba api. Ez…® gumaziba Ahap…®n akam inigha iza a m…®gei. Ez…® an akar kam baregha uan m…®dorozir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, e d…®kavigh mang…® Samariaba ko m…®sogham. Egha me uan averpeniba ategha zui.\f + \fr 20:12 \ft Gumazir maba ghaze, Hibrun akam ves 12 ko ves 16…®n itir Sukot…®n nguibar ekiam m…®gei. Ez…® gumazir maba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, a m…®dorozir gumazibar averpenibav gei.\f* 
