\v 17 Egha Benhadat m…®dorozir gumazir maba amangiz…®, me moga Israelian ganasa ghue. Egha me Israelian m…®dorozir gumazir igiar kabar garima me izi. Ez…® me uamategha ghua Benhadat m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir maba Samarian nguibar ekiam ategha izi.‚Äù 
