\v 22 Ez…® g…®n, akam inigha izir gumazim, Atrivim Ahap bagha ghugha ua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúSiriabar atrivim azenir munam…®n ua iz…® ia ko m…®sogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® ua mang…® uan m…®dorozir gumaziba gavgavim me dan…®ng, egh Siriaba ko m…®soghs…® deragh n…®ghn…®gh ik…®.‚Äù 
\s1 Siriaba ua Israelia ko m…®sosi 
\p  
\v 23 Ez…® g…®n Atrivim Benhadat…®n gumazir dapaniba kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIsraelian aseba, da m…®ghs…®abar aseba. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, aser kaba Israelian akuraz…®, me e ab…®ra. E me ko danganir zaribar uariv sogh, egh guizbang…®ra me ab…®nigham.  
\v 24 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® kamagh…®n damu: N…® atrivir kaba faragh me batueght…®, me ua n…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar faragh mangan mark…®. N…® uan m…®dorozir gumazibar faragh mangamin gumazir dapanitaba am…®sefegh.  
\v 25 Egh n…® uaghan gumazir av…®riba inight…®, me n…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar ik…®t…®, n…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba fom…®ra av…®rasemez…® mogh…®n ikiam. Egh e mang…® danganir zarim…®n Israelia m…®sogh, me ab…®nigham.‚Äù Ez…® Atrivim Benhadat akar kam baregha, me m…®kemez…® mogh…®rama ami. 
