\v 27 Ez…® Israelian atrivim uan m…®dorozir gumazibar diaz…®, me iza uari akuvagha, m…®dorozir bizibar k…®ri. Egha me ghua danganir Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba itim…®n borogh…®ra ghugha, danganir pumuning aghuigha aning…®n iti. Israelian ik…®zim, a bar suvigha, mati memen okoruar bar muziarir pumuning. Ez…® Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba bar av…®rasemegha tintinibar danganiba bar dar iti. 
