\v 31 Ez…® an gumazir dapaniba ghua an ganigha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE kamagh…®n akam baraki, Israelian atriviba, me apangkuvim itir gumaziba. Egha e kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, e azirakar korotiabar aghuigh, benibar uan f…®ribar afegh Israelian atrivim bagh mangam. E kamagh…®n damight…®, a ti n…®n apangkuvigham, egh n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremeghan kogham.‚Äù 
