\v 37 Ez…® g…®n akam inigha izir gumazir kam, gumazir igharazim bagha ghua, kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® na m…®soghasa k…® ifonge.‚Äù Ez…® gumazir kam a m…®sogha, m…®zazir kuram a gasegha an m…®karzim gas…®ghas…®ki.  
\v 38 Ez…® akam inigha izir gumazir kam, nir av…®zir mam isa uan guam avara, eght…® gumazamiziba a g…®foghan kogham.\f + \fr 20:38 \ft Akam inigha izir gumazir maba, ababanir maba uan guabagh ar…®si. Ez…® akam inigha izir gumazir kam, ababanir kam modi. N…® Esekiel 9:4…®n gan.\f* Egha an Atrivim Ahap…®n m…®zua tuavir m…®riam…®n tughav iti. 
\p  
\v 39 Ez…® atrivim izima, akam inigha izir gumazim an diagha ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim, k…® m…®dorozir ekiam…®n aven itima, en m…®dorozir gumazir mam, apanir mam inigha iza na m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄòN…® deraghv…®ra gumazir kam…®n gan. An ar…®mang…®ght…®, k…® n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremegham. Puvat…®ght…®ma, k…® n…® damut…®, n…® 30,000plan kina is…® uan ik…®r…®m…®rim uam a givezam.‚Äô M…®dorozir gumazir kam na m…®kemegha ghu.  
\v 40 Ez…® Atrivim, k…® ghua ingangarir av…®rir igharazibagh amua itima, gumazir kam arav ghu.‚Äù 
