\p  
\v 34 M…®dorozim ghuav…®ra itima, Sirian m…®dorozir gumazir mam, uan barir pim…®n Israelia iti nagh…®n puram asavamada. Ez…® barim ghua Ahap…®n m…®karzir m…®dorozir korotiam avarazir puvat…®zim gasara. Ez…® Ahap uan karis…®n suizir gumazim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ikuvigha g…®fa. N…® zuam…®ra ua karis giragh m…®dorozir danganim atakigh.‚Äù  
\v 35 Ez…® m…®dorozim ghuav…®ra ikia bar gavgaviz…®, Atrivim Ahap m…®dorozim ategh mangan iburaghburaghiz…®, me karis…®n aven puram anefaz…®, a Siriabar damazim…®n uan karis…®n aven aperaghav ikia Siriabar gari. Ez…® an duar torim ghuzim puv…®ra ivemara izaghira karis giz…®vagha, kamagh…®ra itima, aruem gevima an areme. 
\p  
\v 36 Aruem ghuaghira m…®goroghasava amima, Israelia ko Judan m…®dorozir gumaziba me bar d…®a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE bar mogh…®ra uamategh uan kantriba ko uan nguibabar mangam!‚Äù 
\p  
\v 37 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Atrivim Ahap aremez…®, me an kuam inigha ghua Samarian anefa.  
\v 38 Egha an karis, Samarian d…®par akarer mam…®n a rue. Ez…® afiaba izava an ghuzim apima, tuavim…®n amiziba izava an ghuzim itir d…®par akarem gure. Bizir kaba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n otifi.  
\v 39 Atrivim Ahap amizir araziba bar, da ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n aven iti, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. Ak…®nafarir kam, d…®penir a ingarigha elefan…®n ataribar as…®ngiziba ko, an nguibar ekiaba av…®nizir d…®vaziba gavgavim dagh an…®ngizir ingangarir amizibagh eghari.  
\v 40 Ahap uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, an otarim Ahasia an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. 
\s1 Jehosafat Judan atrivim…®n oto 
\r (2 Eghaghaniba 20:31--21:1) 
\p  
\v 41 Ahap Israelian atrivim…®n itima, an namba 4 azenim…®n aven Asan otarim Jehosafat Judan atrivim…®n oto.  
\v 42 Jehosafat azenir 35plan ikia atrivim…®n oto, egha 25plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti. An amebam, Silhin guivim, an ziam Asuba.  
\v 43 Jehosafat uan afeziam Asa faragha ikiava amiz…® mogh…®n, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh ami. Egha bizir vam…®ra, an a gamizir puvat…®, a m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir asebar ziaba fer danganibagh as…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamiziba danganir kabar ofabagh amua, egha pauran mughuriar aghuim zuiba tue.  
\v 44 Jehosafat uaghan Israelian atrivim ko aning uan dafarimning suiragha, aning deraghav…®ra aperaghav ikia, ua uaning m…®sozir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 45 Atrivim Jehosafat amizir araziba bar, da ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n aven iti, Judan Atrivibar Eghaghaniba. Ak…®nafarir kam, a uan apanibav soghezir eghaghaniba ko, an gavgavir ekiabar eghaghaniba an aven iti.  
\v 46 Fom…®ra Jehosafat…®n afeziam Asa, asebar ziaba fer danganibar, gumazir poroghamiba uari bak…®a uari koma akuir arazim gamiba batoke. Ez…® men marazi ikiav…®ra itima, Jehosafat bar me ag…®fa. 
\p  
\v 47 Dughiar kam…®n, Idom…®n kantri atriviba puvat…®. Ez…® Judan atrivimra Idom…®n kantri gativagh, an ganasa gumaziba am…®sefi. 
\p  
\v 48 Atrivim Jehosafat m…®kemez…®, ingangarir gumaziba kantri Ofir…®n mangamin kuribar ingari, eght…® da ongarim…®n mang…® kantri Ofir…®n gol inigh izam. Ez…® kurir kaba, da nguibar ekiam Esiongeber…®n ikuvigha, puram apiaghav iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me Ofir…®n ghuzir puvat…®.  
\v 49 Ez…® g…®n, Israelian Atrivim Ahasia kamagh…®n oraki, Jehosafat…®n kuriba ikufi, ez…® a kamagh…®n Jehosafat m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan kuriba ua da amangight…®, k…® uan kurim…®n ingangarir gumaziba, n…®n ingangarir gumaziba ko me amadaght…® me mangam.‚Äù Ez…® Jehosafat an n…®ghn…®zim…®n aghua. 
\p  
\v 50 Egha g…®n Atrivim Jehosafat uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®ma, me an kuam isa Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n, an inazir afeziabar kuaba afezir danganim…®n anefa. Ez…® an otarim Jehoram an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. 
\s1 Ahasia, Israelian atrivim…®n oto 
\p  
\v 51 Jehosafat Judan atrivim…®n itima, an namba 17…®n azenim…®n aven, Ahap…®n otarim Ahasia Israelian atrivim…®n oto. Egha azenir pumuning…®n Samarian atrivim…®n ike.  
\v 52 A uan afeziam ko amebam…®n m…®n arazir kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dar g…®n ghua, Nebat…®n otarim Jeroboam…®n m…®n ami. Jeroboam faragha Israelia gekuiz…®, me arazir kurar av…®ribagh ami.  
\v 53 Ahasia, asem Bal…®n ziam fe. An arazir kam bang…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, an afeziam Ahap…®n an…®ngaghez…® mogh…®n, an an…®ngaghe.